<!doctype lake><title>玄铁 (XuanTie) 语言指南</title><meta name="doc-version" content="1" /><meta name="viewport" content="fixed" /><meta name="typography" content="classic" /><meta name="paragraphSpacing" content="relax" /><p data-lake-id="u1c852834" id="u1c852834"><span data-lake-id="ua77029a2" id="ua77029a2">玄铁是一门旨在融合“高熵信息含量”与“原生异步并发”特性的中文编程语言。它既能让 AI 更直观地理解逻辑因果，也为中文开发者提供了极高的表达效率。</span></p><p data-lake-id="uac4b5b0c" id="uac4b5b0c"><a href="https://www.yuque.com/markjy/upsxwh/pz1wdzpfhxhvceap" data-lake-id="udec66633" id="udec66633"><span data-lake-id="u08043a52" id="u08043a52">玄铁历史版本更新说明</span></a><span data-lake-id="u89848271" id="u89848271"> | </span><a href="https://www.yuque.com/markjy/upsxwh/lxvtk51lholbxzyw" data-lake-id="udd5931ad" id="udd5931ad"><span data-lake-id="u02746bb6" id="u02746bb6">自举技术架构与底层原理白皮书</span></a><span data-lake-id="u1a379c48" id="u1a379c48"> | </span><a href="https://github.com/MARKJY-China/XuanTie-Lang" target="_blank" data-lake-id="u60cd5c8d" id="u60cd5c8d"><span data-lake-id="u10a0135c" id="u10a0135c">Github开源仓库</span></a><span data-lake-id="u78ff8f8c" id="u78ff8f8c"> | </span><a href="https://gitee.com/mark-jy" target="_blank" data-lake-id="uaa992cb8" id="uaa992cb8"><span data-lake-id="uc2643bb3" id="uc2643bb3">作者-问号盒</span></a></p><p data-lake-id="u3db53fed" id="u3db53fed" style="text-align: left"><card type="inline" name="image" value="data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2026%2Fpng%2F58870876%2F1775411828011-323dafb5-eab6-48ec-8b4f-7cb2d962a03b.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u14124494-3677-4ff0-b830-63b1ca6a6b9%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22uec3cc851-5d20-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22binary%22%2C%22width%22%3A250%2C%22height%22%3A250%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22big-code-icon.png%22%2C%22size%22%3A4339954%2C%22from%22%3A%22ui%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A2048%2C%22originHeight%22%3A2048%2C%22ratio%22%3A1%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23fcfaf9%22%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u170878b8%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card></p><h2 data-lake-id="lxHJE" id="lxHJE"><span data-lake-id="u0733330a" id="u0733330a">1. 基础语法</span></h2><h3 data-lake-id="vA252" id="vA252"><span data-lake-id="u66c8ccdd" id="u66c8ccdd">变量与常量</span></h3><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22java%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%E8%AE%BE%20%E5%90%8D%E5%AD%97%20%3D%20%5C%22%E7%8E%84%E9%93%81%5C%22%5Cn%E5%B8%B8%20%E7%89%88%E6%9C%AC%20%3D%200.13%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Atrue%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22id%22%3A%22PhY9Q%22%7D"></card><h3 data-lake-id="PxXKh" id="PxXKh"><span data-lake-id="u13bc8fe6" id="u13bc8fe6">字符串插值 (String Interpolation)</span></h3><p data-lake-id="u8fae1459" id="u8fae1459"><span data-lake-id="uba39ab60" id="uba39ab60">玄铁支持在字符串中使用 </span><code data-lake-id="u3032e05d" id="u3032e05d"><span data-lake-id="u213824f5" id="u213824f5">#{表达式}</span></code><span data-lake-id="u429f648f" id="u429f648f"> 进行变量或逻辑插值，这比使用 </span><code data-lake-id="u673c8ddb" id="u673c8ddb"><span data-lake-id="u71bb21b5" id="u71bb21b5">&amp;</span></code><span data-lake-id="u8b77e28d" id="u8b77e28d"> 拼接更加简洁。</span></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22java%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%E8%AE%BE%20%E4%BA%BA%20%3D%20%5C%22%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91%E8%80%85%5C%22%5Cn%E7%A4%BA(%5C%22%E4%BD%A0%E5%A5%BD%EF%BC%8C%23%7B%E4%BA%BA%7D%EF%BC%81%E7%8E%B0%E5%9C%A8%E6%98%AF%20%23%7B%E6%97%B6.%E7%8E%B0()%7D%20%E6%AF%AB%E7%A7%92%5C%22)%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Atrue%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22id%22%3A%22cCuWM%22%7D"></card><p data-lake-id="u1401c417" id="u1401c417"><br></p><h3 data-lake-id="jcdkK" id="jcdkK"><span data-lake-id="u56a58504" id="u56a58504">类型转换</span></h3><p data-lake-id="u98e8ed0b" id="u98e8ed0b"><span data-lake-id="u1d012e44" id="u1d012e44">玄铁提供内置函数进行类型强制转换，转换结果始终封装在 `结果` (Result) 中：</span></p><ul list="u8b30e765"><li fid="u03bb7e97" data-lake-id="u4f40a86b" id="u4f40a86b"><code data-lake-id="ua6b79c3a" id="ua6b79c3a"><span data-lake-id="uc004ab41" id="uc004ab41">整(x)</span></code><span data-lake-id="ua2494ad1" id="ua2494ad1">: 转换为整数。如果是字符串且格式不对，返回 </span><code data-lake-id="uef24f87d" id="uef24f87d"><span data-lake-id="u9d95bbb5" id="u9d95bbb5">结果</span></code><span data-lake-id="u67e7dbda" id="u67e7dbda">。</span></li><li fid="u03bb7e97" data-lake-id="u19d8b624" id="u19d8b624"><code data-lake-id="u9e248752" id="u9e248752"><span data-lake-id="ufd1d3076" id="ufd1d3076">小数(x)</span></code><span data-lake-id="u56212f1c" id="u56212f1c">: 转换为小数。</span></li><li fid="u03bb7e97" data-lake-id="u12cd0253" id="u12cd0253"><code data-lake-id="ua5644b9d" id="ua5644b9d"><span data-lake-id="u23d3e1fe" id="u23d3e1fe">字(x)</span></code><span data-lake-id="u43a4ca19" id="u43a4ca19">: 转换为字符串。</span></li></ul><p data-lake-id="u254de8ba" id="u254de8ba"><strong><span data-lake-id="uf7f519b0" id="uf7f519b0">转换安全指南</span></strong><span data-lake-id="uaa71d3c5" id="uaa71d3c5">:<br /></span><span data-lake-id="u309d1477" id="u309d1477">若转换失败（如 </span><code data-lake-id="u60fbbae3" id="u60fbbae3"><span data-lake-id="u2e02ae75" id="u2e02ae75">整(&quot;abc&quot;)</span></code><span data-lake-id="uba8372ab" id="uba8372ab">），结果容器将标记为失败：</span></p><ul list="u5ad507c6"><li fid="uf250d921" data-lake-id="u136f19e7" id="u136f19e7"><span data-lake-id="uacbabebb" id="uacbabebb">直接访问 </span><code data-lake-id="ub0593543" id="ub0593543"><span data-lake-id="u2cbfcbb0" id="u2cbfcbb0">.值</span></code><span data-lake-id="u7e224d29" id="u7e224d29"> 将返回 </span><code data-lake-id="u5e665b21" id="u5e665b21"><span data-lake-id="ud75029e4" id="ud75029e4">空</span></code><span data-lake-id="u4c9098ae" id="u4c9098ae"> (Null)。</span></li><li fid="uf250d921" data-lake-id="ua1023810" id="ua1023810"><span data-lake-id="u65c7a0ff" id="u65c7a0ff">推荐使用 </span><code data-lake-id="ua1a055de" id="ua1a055de"><span data-lake-id="u676d0d73" id="u676d0d73">.或(默认值)</span></code><span data-lake-id="ub95b2c5b" id="ub95b2c5b"> 或 </span><code data-lake-id="u8d789786" id="u8d789786"><span data-lake-id="u620292c6" id="u620292c6">.解包()</span></code><span data-lake-id="u23b80ace" id="u23b80ace"> 进行安全处理。</span></li></ul><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22java%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%E8%AE%BE%20s%20%3D%20%5C%22123%5C%22%5Cn%E8%AE%BE%20n%20%3D%20%E6%95%B4(s).%E5%80%BC%20%2F%2F%20123%5Cn%E8%AE%BE%20f%20%3D%20%E5%B0%8F%E6%95%B0(n).%E5%80%BC%20%2F%2F%20123.0%5Cn%2F%2F%20---%5Cn%E8%AE%BE%20n%20%3D%20%E6%95%B4(s).%E8%A7%A3%E5%8C%85()%20%2F%2F%20123%EF%BC%8C%E8%8B%A5%E5%A4%B1%E8%B4%A5%E5%88%99%E6%8A%9B%E5%87%BA%E5%BC%82%E5%B8%B8%5Cn%E8%AE%BE%20f%20%3D%20%E5%B0%8F%E6%95%B0(%5C%22abc%5C%22).%E6%88%96(0.0)%20%2F%2F%200.0%EF%BC%8C%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E9%99%8D%E7%BA%A7%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Atrue%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22id%22%3A%22SRoRQ%22%7D"></card><p data-lake-id="uf7dd2992" id="uf7dd2992"><br></p><h3 data-lake-id="D1XLw" id="D1XLw"><span data-lake-id="uaef823c3" id="uaef823c3">示出与输入</span></h3><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22java%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%E7%A4%BA(%5C%22%E4%BD%A0%E5%A5%BD%EF%BC%8C%5C%22%20%26%20%E5%90%8D%E5%AD%97)%20%20%2F%2F%20%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%20%26%20%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E5%AD%97%E7%AC%A6%E4%B8%B2%E6%8B%BC%E6%8E%A5%5Cn%E8%AE%BE%20%E5%9B%9E%E5%A4%8D%20%3D%20%E8%BE%93(%5C%22%E8%AF%B7%E8%BE%93%E5%85%A5%EF%BC%9A%5C%22)%20%2F%2F%20%E8%8E%B7%E5%8F%96%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B7%E8%BE%93%E5%85%A5%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Atrue%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22id%22%3A%22z4zrc%22%7D"></card><p data-lake-id="u14ddb924" id="u14ddb924"><br></p><h3 data-lake-id="GIyZA" id="GIyZA"><span data-lake-id="ua357e4b3" id="ua357e4b3">结果容器 (Result) 增强</span></h3><p data-lake-id="u0cdf1356" id="u0cdf1356"><code data-lake-id="u9efae38c" id="u9efae38c"><span data-lake-id="u546e1c70" id="u546e1c70">结果</span></code><span data-lake-id="u889e59f6" id="u889e59f6"> 类型是玄铁错误处理的核心。除了 </span><code data-lake-id="ua538f4a9" id="ua538f4a9"><span data-lake-id="u19e5e270" id="u19e5e270">.成功</span></code><span data-lake-id="ucdc1d447" id="ucdc1d447">、</span><code data-lake-id="u2db47196" id="u2db47196"><span data-lake-id="u72af39da" id="u72af39da">.值</span></code><span data-lake-id="u3c0229df" id="u3c0229df">、</span><code data-lake-id="u111b5a2b" id="u111b5a2b"><span data-lake-id="uef6be964" id="uef6be964">.错误</span></code><span data-lake-id="ud4d453c5" id="ud4d453c5"> 属性外，</span><strong><span data-lake-id="u327e739a" id="u327e739a" style="color: #E4495B">v0.12.0</span></strong><span data-lake-id="u581c02e8" id="u581c02e8"> 引入了完整的函数式组合能力：</span></p><ul list="u5c97b42c"><li fid="ue2eca481" data-lake-id="u47cde56b" id="u47cde56b"><code data-lake-id="ufe3662ce" id="ufe3662ce"><span data-lake-id="u918cec92" id="u918cec92">.接着(函)</span></code><strong><span data-lake-id="u5a4ba550" id="u5a4ba550"> (Then)</span></strong><span data-lake-id="u6d95abf1" id="u6d95abf1">：成功时执行，支持转换容器状态。</span></li><li fid="ue2eca481" data-lake-id="u729716cc" id="u729716cc"><code data-lake-id="u24f2a74b" id="u24f2a74b"><span data-lake-id="u09c9f4c0" id="u09c9f4c0">.映射(函)</span></code><strong><span data-lake-id="u189e0428" id="u189e0428"> (Map)</span></strong><span data-lake-id="ubc5e9380" id="ubc5e9380">：成功时转换值，但不改变成功状态。</span></li><li fid="ue2eca481" data-lake-id="u4e755ca1" id="u4e755ca1"><code data-lake-id="u0146f24c" id="u0146f24c"><span data-lake-id="uf2f9524a" id="uf2f9524a">.否则(函)</span></code><strong><span data-lake-id="u19236171" id="u19236171"> (Catch)</span></strong><span data-lake-id="uf49354fc" id="uf49354fc">：失败时执行。</span></li><li fid="ue2eca481" data-lake-id="u8c5fdb20" id="u8c5fdb20"><code data-lake-id="u3306cba4" id="u3306cba4"><span data-lake-id="u91338797" id="u91338797">.复原(函)</span></code><strong><span data-lake-id="ud6679082" id="ud6679082"> (Recover)</span></strong><span data-lake-id="ud58a6d31" id="ud58a6d31">：失败时尝试恢复，将错误转为成功值。</span></li><li fid="ue2eca481" data-lake-id="uebd50705" id="uebd50705"><code data-lake-id="u70024520" id="u70024520"><span data-lake-id="u9ea171ec" id="u9ea171ec">.执行(函)</span></code><strong><span data-lake-id="u8b318d00" id="u8b318d00"> (Finally)</span></strong><span data-lake-id="uccbcb553" id="uccbcb553">：无论成功失败均执行。</span></li><li fid="ue2eca481" data-lake-id="udd835072" id="udd835072"><code data-lake-id="u9718f622" id="u9718f622"><span data-lake-id="u23f8fbb4" id="u23f8fbb4">.解包()</span></code><strong><span data-lake-id="ude4f05c1" id="ude4f05c1"> / </span></strong><code data-lake-id="u514d7797" id="u514d7797"><span data-lake-id="u3e9a0c65" id="u3e9a0c65">.断言()</span></code><strong><span data-lake-id="u062183f1" id="u062183f1"> (Unwrap)</span></strong><span data-lake-id="u7aabab9a" id="u7aabab9a">：成功则返回值，失败则立即抛出运行时错误。</span></li><li fid="ue2eca481" data-lake-id="uf342b0e8" id="uf342b0e8"><code data-lake-id="uef061a32" id="uef061a32"><span data-lake-id="u9558fda8" id="u9558fda8">.或(默认值)</span></code><strong><span data-lake-id="u87278b26" id="u87278b26"> (GetOrElse)</span></strong><span data-lake-id="u4b45a28c" id="u4b45a28c">：成功则返回值，失败则返回提供的默认值。</span></li></ul><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22java%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%E8%AE%BE%20%E8%8E%B7%E5%8F%96%E6%95%B0%E5%AD%97%20%3D%20%E5%87%BD(s)%20%7B%20%E8%BF%94%20%E6%95%B4(s)%20%7D%5Cn%5Cn%2F%2F%20%E9%93%BE%E5%BC%8F%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86%E7%A4%BA%E4%BE%8B%5Cn%E8%AE%BE%20%E6%9C%80%E7%BB%88%E5%80%BC%20%3D%20%E8%8E%B7%E5%8F%96%E6%95%B0%E5%AD%97(%5C%22123%5C%22)%5Cn.%E6%98%A0%E5%B0%84(%E5%87%BD(x)%20%7B%20%E8%BF%94%20x%20*%202%20%7D)%5Cn.%E5%A4%8D%E5%8E%9F(%E5%87%BD(e)%20%7B%20%E8%BF%94%200%20%7D)%5Cn.%E6%88%96(-1)%5Cn%5Cn%E7%A4%BA(%E6%9C%80%E7%BB%88%E5%80%BC)%20%2F%2F%20246%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Atrue%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22id%22%3A%22awxjn%22%7D"></card><p data-lake-id="uc60c8c2c" id="uc60c8c2c"><br></p><p data-lake-id="u90454eb8" id="u90454eb8"><br></p><h2 data-lake-id="kxPbh" id="kxPbh"><span data-lake-id="uc587bd4e" id="uc587bd4e">2. 数据类型</span></h2><ul list="uc97ace9c"><li fid="u9d9d406e" data-lake-id="u7644f146" id="u7644f146"><strong><span data-lake-id="uab3786e4" id="uab3786e4">基础</span></strong><span data-lake-id="u6b4fa10b" id="u6b4fa10b">: </span><code data-lake-id="uf441e7ea" id="uf441e7ea"><span data-lake-id="u95a08503" id="u95a08503">整</span></code><span data-lake-id="ucc10008a" id="ucc10008a"> (123), </span><code data-lake-id="u1cd78d81" id="u1cd78d81"><span data-lake-id="ufceea20a" id="ufceea20a">小数</span></code><span data-lake-id="u126cd244" id="u126cd244"> (3.14), </span><code data-lake-id="ubccfe463" id="ubccfe463"><span data-lake-id="uc33500f4" id="uc33500f4">字</span></code><span data-lake-id="u1c32b47f" id="u1c32b47f"> (&quot;abc&quot;), </span><code data-lake-id="u7e30b5ab" id="u7e30b5ab"><span data-lake-id="u9d158b0e" id="u9d158b0e">逻</span></code><span data-lake-id="ud9191934" id="ud9191934"> (真/假), </span><code data-lake-id="uad7e3cdb" id="uad7e3cdb"><span data-lake-id="u11c4cb4d" id="u11c4cb4d">空</span></code><span data-lake-id="u48bb6f7a" id="u48bb6f7a"> (空)</span></li><li fid="u9d9d406e" data-lake-id="ua947fbcb" id="ua947fbcb"><strong><span data-lake-id="u50927691" id="u50927691">容器</span></strong><span data-lake-id="uea5466e2" id="uea5466e2">: </span><code data-lake-id="ueead8b82" id="ueead8b82"><span data-lake-id="u97bed8cf" id="u97bed8cf">数组</span></code><span data-lake-id="u66d5640f" id="u66d5640f"> ([1, 2, 3]), </span><code data-lake-id="ua914e3c1" id="ua914e3c1"><span data-lake-id="u2f805108" id="u2f805108">字典</span></code><span data-lake-id="u2a8389d8" id="u2a8389d8"> ({&quot;键&quot;: &quot;值&quot;})</span></li><li fid="u9d9d406e" data-lake-id="u3c30d63e" id="u3c30d63e"><strong><span data-lake-id="u3d52bb58" id="u3d52bb58">结果</span></strong><span data-lake-id="ua0f40594" id="ua0f40594">: </span><code data-lake-id="u2a86fdfd" id="u2a86fdfd"><span data-lake-id="u6b263db0" id="u6b263db0">结果</span></code><span data-lake-id="u9c01e39c" id="u9c01e39c"> (Result) —— 用于错误处理，通过内置函数 </span><code data-lake-id="ub7eb1299" id="ub7eb1299"><span data-lake-id="u7437a490" id="u7437a490">成功(值)</span></code><span data-lake-id="u6db77d4e" id="u6db77d4e"> 或 </span><code data-lake-id="u6898d4d5" id="u6898d4d5"><span data-lake-id="ube1308d8" id="ube1308d8">失败(错误)</span></code><span data-lake-id="uee732376" id="uee732376"> 创建。</span></li><li fid="u9d9d406e" data-lake-id="ub339a823" id="ub339a823"><strong><span data-lake-id="u227b925d" id="u227b925d">进阶</span></strong><span data-lake-id="u062faf99" id="u062faf99">: </span><code data-lake-id="u496fbdb4" id="u496fbdb4"><span data-lake-id="u2db03c6e" id="u2db03c6e">任务</span></code><span data-lake-id="u3a5ce298" id="u3a5ce298"> (Task), </span><code data-lake-id="u13d5d8a4" id="u13d5d8a4"><span data-lake-id="u77d926b7" id="u77d926b7">字节</span></code><span data-lake-id="ubebbd220" id="ubebbd220"> (Bytes)</span></li></ul><h3 data-lake-id="OcIf5" id="OcIf5"><span data-lake-id="u15e4fc68" id="u15e4fc68">类型推导与 FFI 增强 (v0.15.6)</span></h3><p data-lake-id="ue4f2d187" id="ue4f2d187"><span data-lake-id="udf62c171" id="udf62c171">玄铁进一步简化了类型系统的使用，并增强了底层交互能力。</span></p><ul list="u9c09edfa"><li fid="ufe290d70" data-lake-id="u9a83a27e" id="u9a83a27e"><strong><span data-lake-id="u930965e2" id="u930965e2">自动类型推导</span></strong><span data-lake-id="u6a249ee7" id="u6a249ee7">: 声明变量时可省略类型注解，编译器将根据初始值自动推断。</span></li><li fid="ufe290d70" data-lake-id="u6423df31" id="u6423df31"><strong><span data-lake-id="uf58caade" id="uf58caade">泛型语法支持</span></strong><span data-lake-id="u9d39ed8c" id="u9d39ed8c">: 支持在 </span><code data-lake-id="u38fe9c50" id="u38fe9c50"><span data-lake-id="udc8c095b" id="udc8c095b">型</span></code><span data-lake-id="uc5fb81df" id="uc5fb81df"> 和 </span><code data-lake-id="u288c0a7d" id="u288c0a7d"><span data-lake-id="u2ded1cac" id="u2ded1cac">函</span></code><span data-lake-id="ue404a674" id="ue404a674"> 中定义泛型参数 </span><code data-lake-id="uc25943b7" id="uc25943b7"><span data-lake-id="ua7cfb8fd" id="ua7cfb8fd">&lt;T, U&gt;</span></code><span data-lake-id="u517b7c93" id="u517b7c93">。</span></li><li fid="ufe290d70" data-lake-id="u6c2a821c" id="u6c2a821c"><strong><span data-lake-id="u4d212a75" id="u4d212a75">外部函数接口 (FFI)</span></strong><span data-lake-id="u0cc1cb5b" id="u0cc1cb5b">: 支持直接使用 </span><code data-lake-id="ud74e7708" id="ud74e7708"><span data-lake-id="uc79e50c1" id="uc79e50c1">外 函</span></code><span data-lake-id="u9bd5eb50" id="u9bd5eb50"> 声明并调用 C 语言原生函数。</span></li><li fid="ufe290d70" data-lake-id="u0c27d08d" id="u0c27d08d"><strong><span data-lake-id="ufdc71e3e" id="ufdc71e3e">Arena 内存管理</span></strong><span data-lake-id="uea77c400" id="uea77c400">: 针对短生命周期高频分配场景（如编译器），支持使用 Arena 内存池一键回收。</span></li></ul><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22java%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%2F%2F%201.%20%E6%B3%9B%E5%9E%8B%E7%B1%BB%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89%5Cn%E5%9E%8B%20%E7%9B%92%E5%AD%90%3CT%3E%20%7B%20%5Cn%20%20%20%20%E8%AE%BE%20%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9%3A%20T%5Cn%20%20%20%20%E5%87%BD%20%E9%80%A0(%E7%89%A9%3A%20T)%20%7B%20%E6%AD%A4.%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9%20%3D%20%E7%89%A9%20%7D%20%5Cn%7D%5Cn%E8%AE%BE%20%E7%9B%92%20%3D%20%E9%80%A0%20%E7%9B%92%E5%AD%90%3C%E6%95%B4%3E(123)%20%5Cn%5Cn%2F%2F%202.%20%E5%A4%96%E9%83%A8%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%E5%A3%B0%E6%98%8E%20(FFI)%5Cn%E5%A4%96%20%E5%87%BD%20printf(%E6%A0%BC%E5%BC%8F%3A%20%E5%AD%97%2C%20%E5%8F%82%E6%95%B0%3A%20%E6%95%B4)%3A%20%E6%95%B4%5Cnprintf(%5C%22%E4%BD%A0%E5%A5%BD%2C%20%25lld%5C%5Cn%5C%22%2C%2042)%5Cn%5Cn%2F%2F%203.%20Arena%20%E5%86%85%E5%AD%98%E6%B1%A0%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%5Cn%E5%A4%96%20%E5%87%BD%20xt_arena_new(%E5%A4%A7%E5%B0%8F%3A%20%E6%95%B4)%3A%20%E6%95%B4%5Cn%E5%A4%96%20%E5%87%BD%20xt_arena_use(%E6%B1%A0%3A%20%E6%95%B4)%5Cn%E5%A4%96%20%E5%87%BD%20xt_arena_destroy(%E6%B1%A0%3A%20%E6%95%B4)%5Cn%5Cn%E8%AE%BE%20%E6%B1%A0%20%3D%20xt_arena_new(1024%20*%201024)%5Cnxt_arena_use(%E6%B1%A0)%20%2F%2F%20%E5%90%8E%E7%BB%AD%E6%89%80%E6%9C%89%E5%88%86%E9%85%8D%E5%9D%87%E5%9C%A8%E6%B1%A0%E4%B8%AD%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%5Cn%2F%2F%20...%20%E6%89%A7%E8%A1%8C%E9%80%BB%E8%BE%91%20...%5Cnxt_arena_destroy(%E6%B1%A0)%20%2F%2F%20%E4%B8%80%E9%94%AE%E5%9B%9E%E6%94%B6%E6%89%80%E6%9C%89%E5%86%85%E5%AD%98%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Atrue%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22id%22%3A%22IOxdt%22%7D"></card><p data-lake-id="u3e95082c" id="u3e95082c"><br></p><p data-lake-id="u2ca069e7" id="u2ca069e7"><br></p><h3 data-lake-id="SxGvn" id="SxGvn"><span data-lake-id="u4e1aced9" id="u4e1aced9">模块化命名空间与文件引入 (v0.14.0)</span></h3><p data-lake-id="u3a95cd4f" id="u3a95cd4f"><span data-lake-id="u7e06bf37" id="u7e06bf37">玄铁支持模块化开发，允许通过 </span><code data-lake-id="ucf4e70c7" id="ucf4e70c7"><span data-lake-id="u2243e869" id="u2243e869">引</span></code><span data-lake-id="u55aea9e8" id="u55aea9e8"> 关键字引入外部文件。</span></p><h4 data-lake-id="aVhAt" id="aVhAt" data-lake-index-type="0"><span data-lake-id="u924c10e5" id="u924c10e5">平铺引入外部文件</span></h4><p data-lake-id="ucd1c2581" id="ucd1c2581"><span data-lake-id="u3ae86778" id="u3ae86778">在最新的自举编译器实现中，</span><code data-lake-id="udfe1882d" id="udfe1882d"><span data-lake-id="uc773db61" id="uc773db61">引</span></code><span data-lake-id="uc05f48fd" id="uc05f48fd"> 的行为类似于 C/C++ 的 </span><code data-lake-id="u74dab543" id="u74dab543"><span data-lake-id="u70c93bc1" id="u70c93bc1">#include</span></code><span data-lake-id="ue9c91d2c" id="ue9c91d2c">，它会将目标文件解析后，将其内部的全局变量、函数和类定义直接“平铺”引入到当前的全局作用域中。因此，</span><strong><span data-lake-id="u384ee85c" id="u384ee85c">不需要</span></strong><span data-lake-id="u93a8b112" id="u93a8b112">将其赋值给变量，也</span><strong><span data-lake-id="ucb55fe6e" id="ucb55fe6e">不需要</span></strong><span data-lake-id="u5f40d9e5" id="u5f40d9e5">使用 </span><code data-lake-id="uc645e6d5" id="uc645e6d5"><span data-lake-id="uc5c7926a" id="uc5c7926a">予</span></code><span data-lake-id="uee94b706" id="uee94b706"> 关键字。</span></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22java%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%2F%2F%20lib.xt%5Cn%E8%AE%BE%20%E5%90%8D%E5%AD%97%20%3D%20%5C%22%E7%8E%84%E9%93%81%E5%BA%93%5C%22%5Cn%5Cn%E5%87%BD%20%E6%8B%9B%E5%91%BC(%E4%BA%BA)%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20%E7%A4%BA(%5C%22%E4%BD%A0%E5%A5%BD%EF%BC%8C%5C%22%20%26%20%E4%BA%BA)%5Cn%7D%5Cn%5Cn%2F%2F%20main.xt%5Cn%E5%BC%95%20%5C%22lib.xt%5C%22%5Cn%5Cn%E7%A4%BA(%E5%90%8D%E5%AD%97)%5Cn%E6%8B%9B%E5%91%BC(%5C%22%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%5C%22)%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Atrue%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22id%22%3A%22AyXRF%22%7D"></card><h4 data-lake-id="wvjoU" id="wvjoU" data-lake-index-type="0"><span data-lake-id="uc995d4cf" id="uc995d4cf">显式命名空间引入 (推荐)</span></h4><p data-lake-id="u2d64a9f4" id="u2d64a9f4"><span data-lake-id="u770528b9" id="u770528b9">为了防止不同文件中出现同名的函数、变量或类产生</span><strong><span data-lake-id="u3e4d295e" id="u3e4d295e">命名冲突</span></strong><span data-lake-id="u32d8cac1" id="u32d8cac1">，玄铁设计了 </span><code data-lake-id="ud63e0c33" id="ud63e0c33"><span data-lake-id="u58e9bc9f" id="u58e9bc9f">予</span></code><span data-lake-id="ub06be1ec" id="ub06be1ec"> 关键字来隔离命名空间：</span></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22java%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%2F%2F%20lib-a.xt%5Cn%E8%AE%BE%20%E5%90%8D%E5%AD%97%20%3D%20%5C%22%E7%8E%84%E9%93%81%E5%BA%93A%5C%22%5Cn%5Cn%E5%87%BD%20%E6%8B%9B%E5%91%BC(%E4%BA%BA)%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20%E7%A4%BA(%5C%22%E4%BD%A0%E5%A5%BD%EF%BC%8C%5C%22%20%26%20%E4%BA%BA)%5Cn%7D%5Cn%2F%2F%20lib-b.xt%5Cn%E8%AE%BE%20%E5%90%8D%E5%AD%97%20%3D%20%5C%22%E7%8E%84%E9%93%81%E5%BA%93B%5C%22%5Cn%5Cn%E5%87%BD%20%E6%8B%9B%E5%91%BC(%E4%BA%BA)%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20%E7%A4%BA(%5C%22%E4%BD%A0%E5%A5%BD%EF%BC%8C%5C%22%20%26%20%E4%BA%BA)%5Cn%7D%5Cn%5Cn%2F%2F%20main.xt%5Cn%E5%BC%95%20%5C%22lib-a.xt%5C%22%20%E4%BA%88%20%E4%B8%80%E5%8F%B7%E5%BA%93%5Cn%E5%BC%95%20%5C%22lib-b.xt%5C%22%20%E4%BA%88%20%E4%BA%8C%E5%8F%B7%E5%BA%93%5Cn%5Cn%E7%A4%BA(%E5%90%8D%E5%AD%97)%5Cn%E4%B8%80%E5%8F%B7%E5%BA%93.%E6%8B%9B%E5%91%BC(%5C%22%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%5C%22)%5Cn%E4%BA%8C%E5%8F%B7%E5%BA%93.%E6%8B%9B%E5%91%BC(%5C%22%E5%AE%87%E5%AE%99%5C%22)%5Cn%5Cn%2F%2F%E8%BE%93%E5%87%BA%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9%5Cn%5C%22%E4%BD%A0%E5%A5%BD%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%5C%22%5Cn%5C%22%E4%BD%A0%E5%A5%BD%EF%BC%8C%E5%AE%87%E5%AE%99%5C%22%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Atrue%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22fontSize%22%3A14%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22__spacing%22%3A%22both%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22MSD8Z%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D"></card><p data-lake-id="u80bbbad8" id="u80bbbad8"><br></p><p data-lake-id="uab0788f9" id="uab0788f9"><br></p><h3 data-lake-id="OsMEK" id="OsMEK"><span data-lake-id="u2984eda1" id="u2984eda1">类型注解 (v0.9.8)</span></h3><p data-lake-id="u9359d28e" id="u9359d28e"><span data-lake-id="u98d90889" id="u98d90889">玄铁支持</span><strong><span data-lake-id="u2a715b80" id="u2a715b80">可选类型注解</span></strong><span data-lake-id="u593f7674" id="u593f7674">，允许在声明变量、定义函数参数或指定函数返回值时，明确其预期的类型。</span></p><ul list="u2d80cd34"><li fid="u46d22b2a" data-lake-id="uc05b4bb6" id="uc05b4bb6"><strong><span data-lake-id="ue24825bf" id="ue24825bf">基础注解</span></strong><span data-lake-id="u0d420fda" id="u0d420fda">: </span><code data-lake-id="u3a5a7811" id="u3a5a7811"><span data-lake-id="u78f83ec5" id="u78f83ec5" style="color: #ED740C">设</span><span data-lake-id="u0d7af3b5" id="u0d7af3b5"> 变量: 类型 = 值</span></code></li><li fid="u46d22b2a" data-lake-id="u19f94636" id="u19f94636"><strong><span data-lake-id="u9395d6d1" id="u9395d6d1">联合类型 (Union)</span></strong><span data-lake-id="ubaff7cc5" id="ubaff7cc5">: 使用 </span><code data-lake-id="u5373cc30" id="u5373cc30"><span data-lake-id="u4b35538c" id="u4b35538c">|</span></code><span data-lake-id="u76024ed5" id="u76024ed5"> 表示多种可能类型，如 </span><code data-lake-id="u71612655" id="u71612655"><span data-lake-id="u980ab4fc" id="u980ab4fc" style="color: #ED740C">设</span><span data-lake-id="ue42d3e96" id="ue42d3e96"> 值: 字 | 整 = </span><span data-lake-id="u17ddf921" id="u17ddf921" style="color: #117CEE">123</span></code><span data-lake-id="u581fa1f1" id="u581fa1f1">。</span></li><li fid="u46d22b2a" data-lake-id="u9cffcb81" id="u9cffcb81"><strong><span data-lake-id="ub0053e30" id="ub0053e30">空安全 (Nullable)</span></strong><span data-lake-id="ub371b75c" id="ub371b75c">: 使用 </span><code data-lake-id="uaac77f1a" id="uaac77f1a"><span data-lake-id="u51981daf" id="u51981daf">?</span></code><span data-lake-id="u66325638" id="u66325638"> 表示可为空，如 </span><code data-lake-id="u8c667a45" id="u8c667a45"><span data-lake-id="u87e40856" id="u87e40856" style="color: #ED740C">设</span><span data-lake-id="u0ef5e158" id="u0ef5e158"> 名字: 字? = </span><span data-lake-id="u4b667e58" id="u4b667e58" style="color: #1DC0C9">空</span></code><span data-lake-id="ue6396d93" id="ue6396d93">。未加 </span><code data-lake-id="u3e66ec53" id="u3e66ec53"><span data-lake-id="ub0f9f64d" id="ub0f9f64d">?</span></code><span data-lake-id="ue8d15ed8" id="ue8d15ed8"> 的类型默认不允许赋值为 </span><code data-lake-id="u505b71bf" id="u505b71bf"><span data-lake-id="u6fed7ec9" id="u6fed7ec9" style="color: #1DC0C9">空</span></code><span data-lake-id="ub2e1f3e3" id="ub2e1f3e3">。</span></li><li fid="u46d22b2a" data-lake-id="u1c159b82" id="u1c159b82"><strong><span data-lake-id="u59b1241d" id="u59b1241d">接口 (Interface)</span></strong><span data-lake-id="u20635906" id="u20635906">: 使用 </span><code data-lake-id="uc554a1bc" id="uc554a1bc"><span data-lake-id="u72db0859" id="u72db0859" style="color: #ED740C">口</span></code><span data-lake-id="u90b487fb" id="u90b487fb"> 定义方法契约。类只要实现了接口定义的所有方法，即可被视为该接口类型。</span><strong><span data-lake-id="u0c1c35d9" id="u0c1c35d9">泛</span></strong></li><li fid="u46d22b2a" data-lake-id="u19edfb2c" id="u19edfb2c"><strong><span data-lake-id="u7a4ec2c0" id="u7a4ec2c0">泛型 (Generics)</span></strong><span data-lake-id="uc26632e2" id="uc26632e2">: 使用 </span><code data-lake-id="ue0954487" id="ue0954487"><span data-lake-id="u8382b872" id="u8382b872" style="color: #1DC0C9">&lt;</span><span data-lake-id="u64443c72" id="u64443c72" style="color: #D22D8D">T</span><span data-lake-id="u8eab2f5e" id="u8eab2f5e" style="color: #1DC0C9">&gt;</span></code><span data-lake-id="ucf9c6d19" id="ucf9c6d19"> 定义泛型类或函数，支持类型参数化。支持使用 </span><code data-lake-id="u8056afb8" id="u8056afb8"><span data-lake-id="u1ad2e228" id="u1ad2e228" style="color: #D22D8D">承</span></code><span data-lake-id="uea90d16e" id="uea90d16e"> 进行</span><strong><span data-lake-id="u10d6764e" id="u10d6764e">泛型约束</span></strong><span data-lake-id="ufed2d782" id="ufed2d782">，如 </span><code data-lake-id="u0f7c9ffe" id="u0f7c9ffe"><span data-lake-id="u428ff70e" id="u428ff70e" style="color: #1DC0C9">&lt;</span><span data-lake-id="ua17e2d9c" id="ua17e2d9c" style="color: #D22D8D">T</span><span data-lake-id="uac2f10f5" id="uac2f10f5"> </span><span data-lake-id="uf9546d48" id="uf9546d48" style="color: #D22D8D">承</span><span data-lake-id="ufa44e484" id="ufa44e484"> </span><span data-lake-id="udcedf205" id="udcedf205" style="color: #ED740C">会飞的</span><span data-lake-id="u34192748" id="u34192748" style="color: #1DC0C9">&gt;</span></code><span data-lake-id="u31292443" id="u31292443">。</span></li><li fid="u46d22b2a" data-lake-id="u3cefe723" id="u3cefe723"><strong><span data-lake-id="u0ae96a0d" id="u0ae96a0d">自定义类</span></strong><span data-lake-id="u326fc5c3" id="u326fc5c3">: 支持使用类名作为类型注解。</span></li></ul><p data-lake-id="u5792f4d1" id="u5792f4d1"><span data-lake-id="u0862bfe4" id="u0862bfe4">支持的内置类型：</span><code data-lake-id="u54d0f982" id="u54d0f982"><span data-lake-id="uf0ddd861" id="uf0ddd861">整</span></code><span data-lake-id="ueb89d934" id="ueb89d934">, </span><code data-lake-id="ubf9bab05" id="ubf9bab05"><span data-lake-id="ud42da72a" id="ud42da72a">小数</span></code><span data-lake-id="uea2a6202" id="uea2a6202">, </span><code data-lake-id="u4a9d6930" id="u4a9d6930"><span data-lake-id="u704c3d35" id="u704c3d35">字</span></code><span data-lake-id="u79a41818" id="u79a41818">, </span><code data-lake-id="uc67dce87" id="uc67dce87"><span data-lake-id="uc39adea1" id="uc39adea1">逻</span></code><span data-lake-id="uaa15a85c" id="uaa15a85c">, </span><code data-lake-id="ud43554f5" id="ud43554f5"><span data-lake-id="ua6e5ae70" id="ua6e5ae70">数组</span></code><span data-lake-id="u0dd8d2a5" id="u0dd8d2a5">, </span><code data-lake-id="u45277319" id="u45277319"><span data-lake-id="uf6023607" id="uf6023607">字典</span></code><span data-lake-id="u92a151bb" id="u92a151bb">, </span><code data-lake-id="u77fbb302" id="u77fbb302"><span data-lake-id="uc413a6ca" id="uc413a6ca">字节</span></code><span data-lake-id="u7c97d17c" id="u7c97d17c">, </span><code data-lake-id="u0cbff573" id="u0cbff573"><span data-lake-id="u49e26212" id="u49e26212">结果</span></code><span data-lake-id="u576e116e" id="u576e116e">, </span><code data-lake-id="ub28b1f51" id="ub28b1f51"><span data-lake-id="u8f00ee9f" id="u8f00ee9f">空</span></code><span data-lake-id="u4aabd51e" id="u4aabd51e">。</span></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22java%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%2F%2F%201.%20%E6%B3%9B%E5%9E%8B%E7%B1%BB%5Cn%E5%9E%8B%20%E7%9B%92%E5%AD%90%3CT%3E%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20%E8%AE%BE%20%E5%80%BC%3A%20T%5Cn%20%20%20%20%E5%87%BD%20%E9%80%A0(v%3A%20T)%20%7B%20%E5%80%BC%20%3D%20v%20%7D%5Cn%7D%5Cn%E8%AE%BE%20b%3A%20%E7%9B%92%E5%AD%90%3C%E6%95%B4%3E%20%3D%20%E9%80%A0%20%E7%9B%92%E5%AD%90%3C%E6%95%B4%3E(123)%5Cn%2F%2F%E4%B9%9F%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E8%AE%A9%E8%A7%A3%E9%87%8A%E5%99%A8%E8%87%AA%E5%8A%A8%E6%8E%A8%E5%AF%BC%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B%5Cn%E8%AE%BE%20b%3A%20%E7%9B%92%E5%AD%90%3C%E6%95%B4%3E%20%3D%20%E9%80%A0%20%E7%9B%92%E5%AD%90(123)%5Cn%5Cn%2F%2F%202.%20%E6%B3%9B%E5%9E%8B%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%5Cn%E5%87%BD%20%E6%81%92%E7%AD%89%3CT%3E(x%3A%20T)%3A%20T%20%7B%20%E8%BF%94%20x%20%7D%20%2F%2F%E5%A3%B0%E6%98%8E%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%E2%80%9C%E6%81%92%E7%AD%89%E2%80%9D%E5%B9%B6%E9%9D%99%E6%80%81%E6%8C%87%E5%AE%9A%E8%BF%94%E5%9B%9E%E5%80%BC%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B%E4%B8%BAT%E3%80%81%E5%8F%82%E6%95%B0%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B%E4%B8%BAT%5Cn%E6%81%92%E7%AD%89%3C%E5%AD%97%3E(%5C%22%E4%BD%A0%E5%A5%BD%5C%22)%20%2F%2F%E5%A3%B0%E6%98%8ET%E4%B8%BA%E5%AD%97%E7%AC%A6%E4%B8%B2%E7%B1%BB%E5%9E%8B%E3%80%82%E6%89%A7%E8%A1%8C%E5%90%8E%E4%BC%9A%E6%89%93%E5%8D%B0%E2%80%9C%E4%BD%A0%E5%A5%BD%E2%80%9D%5Cn%5Cn%2F%2F%203.%20%E6%B3%9B%E5%9E%8B%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%2B%E7%BA%A6%E6%9D%9F%5Cn%E5%87%BD%20%E5%90%AF%E5%8A%A8%E9%A3%9E%E8%A1%8C%3CT%20%E6%89%BF%20%E4%BC%9A%E9%A3%9E%E7%9A%84%3E(%E5%99%A8%E7%89%A9%3A%20T)%20%7B%20%2F%2FT%E7%BB%A7%E6%89%BF%E6%A8%A1%E5%9E%8B%E2%80%9C%E4%BC%9A%E9%A3%9E%E7%9A%84%E2%80%9D%EF%BC%8C%E7%A1%AE%E4%BF%9D%E8%83%BD%E9%80%A0%E2%80%9C%E9%B8%9F%E2%80%9D%5Cn%7D%5Cn%E5%90%AF%E5%8A%A8%E9%A3%9E%E8%A1%8C%3C%E9%B8%9F%3E(%E9%80%A0%20%E9%B8%9F())%5Cn%5Cn%2F%2F%204.%20%E6%8E%A5%E5%8F%A3%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89%5Cn%E5%8F%A3%20%E4%BC%9A%E9%A3%9E%E7%9A%84%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20%E5%87%BD%20%E9%A3%9E%E8%A1%8C()%5Cn%7D%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Atrue%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%7B%22from%22%3A65%2C%22to%22%3A66%2C%22color%22%3A%22%2374B602%22%7D%2C%7B%22from%22%3A75%2C%22to%22%3A76%2C%22color%22%3A%22%2374B602%22%7D%5D%2C%22id%22%3A%22swNhg%22%7D"></card><p data-lake-id="u032c6364" id="u032c6364"><br></p><p data-lake-id="u927a2c9a" id="u927a2c9a"><br></p><h3 data-lake-id="Q9nDj" id="Q9nDj"><span data-lake-id="u812428d8" id="u812428d8">索引与属性访问</span></h3><p data-lake-id="u7897bde4" id="u7897bde4"><span data-lake-id="udd530ffa" id="udd530ffa">支持通过 </span><code data-lake-id="u8038c0ad" id="u8038c0ad"><span data-lake-id="u95ca9bf3" id="u95ca9bf3">[]</span></code><span data-lake-id="uf490b382" id="uf490b382"> 访问数组、字典和字符串的元素，支持通过 </span><code data-lake-id="u2fb93583" id="u2fb93583"><span data-lake-id="u7109602d" id="u7109602d">.长度</span></code><span data-lake-id="ue1c1d5a2" id="ue1c1d5a2"> 获取容器大小。</span></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22java%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%E8%AE%BE%20%E6%96%87%E6%9C%AC%20%3D%20%5C%22%E7%8E%84%E9%93%81%5C%22%5Cn%E7%A4%BA(%E6%96%87%E6%9C%AC%5B0%5D)%20%2F%2F%20%E8%BE%93%E5%87%BA%3A%20%E7%8E%84%5Cn%5Cn%E7%A4%BA(%E6%96%87%E6%9C%AC.%E9%95%BF%E5%BA%A6)%20%2F%2F%20%E8%BE%93%E5%87%BA%3A%202%20(UTF-8%20%E5%AD%97%E8%8A%82%E9%95%BF%E5%BA%A6)%5Cn%5Cn%E8%AE%BE%20%E5%88%97%E8%A1%A8%20%3D%20%5B1%2C%202%2C%203%5D%5Cn%E7%A4%BA(%E5%88%97%E8%A1%A8%5B1%5D)%20%2F%2F%20%E8%BE%93%E5%87%BA%3A%202%5Cn%E7%A4%BA(%E5%88%97%E8%A1%A8.%E9%95%BF%E5%BA%A6)%20%2F%2F%20%E8%BE%93%E5%87%BA%3A%203%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Atrue%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22id%22%3A%22bdb4V%22%7D"></card><p data-lake-id="u0846c606" id="u0846c606"><br></p><p data-lake-id="u3ceda260" id="u3ceda260"><br></p><h3 data-lake-id="Z9viu" id="Z9viu"><span data-lake-id="u344a438c" id="u344a438c">数组高级操作 (v0.12.0)</span></h3><p data-lake-id="u81f5483f" id="u81f5483f"><span data-lake-id="u4a96e789" id="u4a96e789">数组现在具备了工业级编程语言的成员方法：</span></p><ul list="ue0a3809d"><li fid="u3889a8be" data-lake-id="udac90a7d" id="udac90a7d"><code data-lake-id="u9a400b85" id="u9a400b85"><span data-lake-id="uc85763e4" id="uc85763e4">.追加(元素1, ...)</span></code><span data-lake-id="ubd87df25" id="ubd87df25">：在末尾添加元素，支持多个。</span></li><li fid="u3889a8be" data-lake-id="uab604a25" id="uab604a25"><code data-lake-id="ufb15a0ec" id="ufb15a0ec"><span data-lake-id="u2b24751a" id="u2b24751a">.截取(起始, [结束])</span></code><span data-lake-id="u6c967b4f" id="u6c967b4f">：截取子数组（不改变原数组）。</span></li><li fid="u3889a8be" data-lake-id="u5c73e3d8" id="u5c73e3d8"><code data-lake-id="u3cac2c7e" id="u3cac2c7e"><span data-lake-id="ud05cb4e8" id="ud05cb4e8">.删(索引)</span></code><span data-lake-id="ud5c6dcb0" id="ud5c6dcb0">：删除指定位置元素。</span></li><li fid="u3889a8be" data-lake-id="uf68c3801" id="uf68c3801"><code data-lake-id="uf51424f0" id="uf51424f0"><span data-lake-id="u94434be2" id="u94434be2">.插(索引, 元素)</span></code><span data-lake-id="u84e1f33e" id="u84e1f33e">：在指定位置插入元素。</span></li><li fid="u3889a8be" data-lake-id="u9443b132" id="u9443b132"><code data-lake-id="u908e6bab" id="u908e6bab"><span data-lake-id="u39998ff1" id="u39998ff1">.包含(元素)</span></code><span data-lake-id="u3cc1144a" id="u3cc1144a"> / </span><code data-lake-id="uaf2851e3" id="uaf2851e3"><span data-lake-id="u911586cb" id="u911586cb">.包含?(元素)</span></code><span data-lake-id="u121c29d1" id="u121c29d1">：判断数组是否包含该元素。</span></li><li fid="u3889a8be" data-lake-id="u1b9cf285" id="u1b9cf285"><code data-lake-id="uf048516a" id="uf048516a"><span data-lake-id="ud7c609e4" id="ud7c609e4">.空?</span></code><span data-lake-id="u2d59ac2d" id="u2d59ac2d"> / </span><code data-lake-id="u38c85da9" id="u38c85da9"><span data-lake-id="ued9e89f3" id="ued9e89f3">.非空?</span></code><span data-lake-id="u60647a68" id="u60647a68">：判断数组状态。</span></li><li fid="u3889a8be" data-lake-id="u50be074d" id="u50be074d"><code data-lake-id="u541c824f" id="u541c824f"><span data-lake-id="uf0bdc60f" id="uf0bdc60f">.映射(回调(x, i))</span></code><span data-lake-id="u0a5e975e" id="u0a5e975e">：返回一个经过回调函数处理后的新数组。</span></li><li fid="u3889a8be" data-lake-id="uc000fa4a" id="uc000fa4a"><code data-lake-id="u34bc377f" id="u34bc377f"><span data-lake-id="u47e1f67f" id="u47e1f67f">.过滤(谓词(x, i))</span></code><span data-lake-id="u1e602ef1" id="u1e602ef1">：返回一个满足条件的元素组成的新数组。</span></li><li fid="u3889a8be" data-lake-id="uc19d2926" id="uc19d2926"><code data-lake-id="u7f943d77" id="u7f943d77"><span data-lake-id="ud69f80f3" id="ud69f80f3">.归纳(回调(累, x, i), [初值])</span></code><span data-lake-id="uc42c334e" id="uc42c334e">：进行累加、拼接等归约操作。</span></li><li fid="u3889a8be" data-lake-id="ub486ecbd" id="ub486ecbd"><code data-lake-id="ua528b0cb" id="ua528b0cb"><span data-lake-id="uf74da680" id="uf74da680">.去重()</span></code><span data-lake-id="ue4d46ab2" id="ue4d46ab2">：去除数组中的重复元素。</span></li><li fid="u3889a8be" data-lake-id="ud749406c" id="ud749406c"><code data-lake-id="u650090bd" id="u650090bd"><span data-lake-id="u44a05c61" id="u44a05c61">.展平()</span></code><span data-lake-id="ubea7e876" id="ubea7e876">：将嵌套数组展开为平铺数组。</span></li><li fid="u3889a8be" data-lake-id="ue5e1ddc6" id="ue5e1ddc6"><code data-lake-id="ua88e7304" id="ua88e7304"><span data-lake-id="u366cd59e" id="u366cd59e">.排序([比较函])</span></code><span data-lake-id="u3a09d72b" id="u3a09d72b">：对数组进行排序。</span></li></ul><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22java%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%E8%AE%BE%20%E5%88%97%E8%A1%A8%20%3D%20%5B1%2C%202%2C%203%5D%5Cn%E5%88%97%E8%A1%A8.%E8%BF%BD%E5%8A%A0(4).%E5%88%A0(0)%20%2F%2F%20%E9%93%BE%E5%BC%8F%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9C%EF%BC%9A%5B2%2C%203%2C%204%5D%5Cn%E8%AE%BE%20%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%9C%20%3D%20%E5%88%97%E8%A1%A8.%E8%BF%87%E6%BB%A4(%E5%87%BD(x)%20%7B%20%E8%BF%94%20x%20%3E%202%20%7D)%20%2F%2F%20%5B3%2C%204%5D%5Cn%5Cn%2F%2F%20-----%5Cn%5Cn%E8%AE%BE%20%E5%88%97%E8%A1%A8%20%3D%20%5B3%2C%201%2C%204%2C%201%5D%5Cn%E8%AE%BE%20%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%9C%20%3D%20%E5%88%97%E8%A1%A8.%E5%8E%BB%E9%87%8D().%E6%8E%92%E5%BA%8F()%20%2F%2F%20%5B1%2C%203%2C%204%5D%5Cn%E8%AE%BE%20%E6%80%BB%E5%92%8C%20%3D%20%E5%88%97%E8%A1%A8.%E5%BD%92%E7%BA%B3(%E5%87%BD(a%2C%20b)%20%7B%20%E8%BF%94%20a%20%2B%20b%20%7D%2C%200)%20%2F%2F%209%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Atrue%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22id%22%3A%22valwc%22%7D"></card><p data-lake-id="u6f501123" id="u6f501123"><br></p><h3 data-lake-id="f6EC1" id="f6EC1"><span data-lake-id="u14c70df2" id="u14c70df2">逻辑运算</span></h3><p data-lake-id="u964da34c" id="u964da34c"><span data-lake-id="ufbc3d503" id="ufbc3d503">支持标准的逻辑运算，并具备</span><strong><span data-lake-id="u3947d505" id="u3947d505">短路求值</span></strong><span data-lake-id="u715c0ac2" id="u715c0ac2">特性。</span></p><ul list="u67110714"><li fid="uabec4b8d" data-lake-id="u5223ddb5" id="u5223ddb5"><code data-lake-id="u67d06b67" id="u67d06b67"><span data-lake-id="ud95c7cc2" id="ud95c7cc2">且</span></code><span data-lake-id="u5e6c2163" id="u5e6c2163"> (AND): 两个条件都为真时结果为真。</span></li><li fid="uabec4b8d" data-lake-id="u92456274" id="u92456274"><code data-lake-id="uc93987e2" id="uc93987e2"><span data-lake-id="u75fa1d87" id="u75fa1d87">或</span></code><span data-lake-id="ub8272d63" id="ub8272d63"> (OR): 其中一个条件为真时结果为真。</span></li><li fid="uabec4b8d" data-lake-id="u72a57bb4" id="u72a57bb4"><code data-lake-id="u1bf1f299" id="u1bf1f299"><span data-lake-id="u4b89063a" id="u4b89063a">非</span></code><span data-lake-id="ucd634634" id="ucd634634"> (NOT): 对逻辑值取反。</span></li><li fid="uabec4b8d" data-lake-id="uf2e166b0" id="uf2e166b0"><code data-lake-id="ua5e1222a" id="ua5e1222a"><span data-lake-id="u2253301c" id="u2253301c">是</span></code><span data-lake-id="udc9aa038" id="udc9aa038"> (IS): 用于判断类型或逻辑相等。</span></li><li fid="uabec4b8d" data-lake-id="u35627d8b" id="u35627d8b"><code data-lake-id="u224aaec5" id="u224aaec5"><span data-lake-id="u0f9a83de" id="u0f9a83de">-</span></code><span data-lake-id="u4fcf4a9c" id="u4fcf4a9c"> (负号): 对数值取反。</span></li></ul><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22java%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%E8%8B%A5%20(1%20%3E%200)%20%E4%B8%94%20(2%20%3E%201)%20%7B%20%E7%A4%BA(%5C%22%E7%9C%9F%5C%22)%20%7D%5Cn%E8%AE%BE%20%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%9C%20%3D%20%E9%9D%9E%20%E7%9C%9F%20%2F%2F%20%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%9C%E4%B8%BA%E5%81%87%5Cn%E8%8B%A5%201%20%E7%AD%89%E4%BA%8E%201%20%7B%20%E7%A4%BA(%5C%22%E4%B8%80%E7%AD%89%E4%BA%8E%E4%B8%80%5C%22)%20%7D%5Cn%E8%8B%A5%201%20%E6%98%AF%20%E6%95%B4%20%7B%20%E7%A4%BA(%5C%221%20%E6%98%AF%E6%95%B4%E6%95%B0%5C%22)%20%7D%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Atrue%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22FCZa0%22%7D"></card><p data-lake-id="u1fbaff4c" id="u1fbaff4c"><br></p><p data-lake-id="u570314a1" id="u570314a1"><br></p><h2 data-lake-id="F13xp" id="F13xp"><span data-lake-id="u2f663948" id="u2f663948">3. 流程控制</span></h2><h3 data-lake-id="YFvc6" id="YFvc6"><span data-lake-id="u28beba4e" id="u28beba4e">条件判断 (若-抑-否)</span></h3><p data-lake-id="uba2a3310" id="uba2a3310"><span data-lake-id="u57b08e32" id="u57b08e32">玄铁采用极其简练的条件控制语法。</span></p><blockquote data-lake-id="ud414d144" id="ud414d144"><p data-lake-id="u19af5fb8" id="u19af5fb8"><code data-lake-id="u522f296e" id="u522f296e"><span data-lake-id="u9e808948" id="u9e808948">抑</span></code><span data-lake-id="u8735bd45" id="u8735bd45">古义为“或者”。在这里，它表示“否则如果条件为真则执行”。</span></p></blockquote><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22java%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%E8%8B%A5%2010%20%3E%205%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20%E7%A4%BA(%5C%22%E6%AD%A3%E7%A1%AE%5C%22)%5Cn%7D%20%E6%8A%91%2010%20%3D%3D%205%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20%E7%A4%BA(%5C%22%E7%AD%89%E4%BA%8E%5C%22)%5Cn%7D%20%E5%90%A6%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20%E7%A4%BA(%5C%22%E9%94%99%E8%AF%AF%5C%22)%5Cn%7D%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Atrue%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22dinpW%22%7D"></card><p data-lake-id="u0490f93f" id="u0490f93f"><br></p><h3 data-lake-id="QoPv9" id="QoPv9"><span data-lake-id="u237e7089" id="u237e7089">循环与遍历</span></h3><p data-lake-id="u2e0027d0" id="u2e0027d0"><span data-lake-id="u7b80592f" id="u7b80592f">玄铁支持条件循环以及针对容器的快速遍历。</span></p><p data-lake-id="ub6552119" id="ub6552119"><strong><span data-lake-id="u742129ab" id="u742129ab">当 (While) 循环</span></strong></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22java%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%E8%AE%BE%20i%20%3D%200%5Cn%E5%BD%93%20i%20%3C%203%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20%E7%A4%BA(i)%5Cn%20%20%20%20i%20%3D%20i%20%2B%201%5Cn%7D%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Atrue%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22WVv4u%22%7D"></card><p data-lake-id="u23c8a883" id="u23c8a883"><strong><span data-lake-id="u77589114" id="u77589114">循 (Loop) 无限循环</span></strong></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22java%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%E8%AE%BE%20k%20%3D%200%5Cn%E5%BE%AA%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20k%20%3D%20k%20%2B%201%5Cn%20%20%20%20%E8%8B%A5%20k%20%3E%2010%20%7B%20%E6%96%AD%20%7D%5Cn%20%20%20%20%2F%2F%E5%A6%82%E6%9E%9Ck%E5%A4%A7%E4%BA%8E10%E9%82%A3%E4%B9%88%E6%96%AD%E5%BC%80%EF%BC%88%E8%B7%B3%E5%87%BA%EF%BC%89%E5%BE%AA%E7%8E%AF%5Cn%7D%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Atrue%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%