4eda"> 语句，支持值匹配、类型匹配和通配符。</span></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22java%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%E8%AE%BE%20x%20%3D%20%5C%22123%5C%22%5Cn%5Cn%E5%8C%B9%E9%85%8D%20x%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%201%20-%3E%20%7B%20%E7%A4%BA(%5C%22%E6%98%AF%E6%95%B0%E5%AD%97%201%5C%22)%20%7D%5Cn%20%20%20%20%5C%22123%5C%22%20-%3E%20%7B%20%E7%A4%BA(%5C%22%E6%98%AF%E5%AD%97%E7%AC%A6%E4%B8%B2%20123%5C%22)%20%7D%5Cn%20%20%20%20%E6%98%AF%20%E6%95%B4%20-%3E%20%7B%20%E7%A4%BA(%5C%22%E6%98%AF%E4%BB%BB%E6%84%8F%E6%95%B4%E6%95%B0%5C%22)%20%7D%5Cn%20%20%20%20_%20-%3E%20%7B%20%E7%A4%BA(%5C%22%E9%BB%98%E8%AE%A4%E5%88%86%E6%94%AF%5C%22)%20%7D%5Cn%7D%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Atrue%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22ug2rC%22%7D"></card><p data-lake-id="ufd30931b" id="ufd30931b"><br></p><h2 data-lake-id="gAcp5" id="gAcp5"><span data-lake-id="u167b9a44" id="u167b9a44">4. 函数</span></h2><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22java%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%E8%AE%BE%20%E5%8A%A0%E6%B3%95%20%3D%20%E5%87%BD(a%2C%20b)%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20%E8%BF%94%20a%20%2B%20b%5Cn%7D%5Cn%E8%AE%BE%20%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%9C%20%3D%20%E5%8A%A0%E6%B3%95(1%2C%202)%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Atrue%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22xsqxk%22%7D"></card><p data-lake-id="ue3252b02" id="ue3252b02"><br></p><p data-lake-id="u9831aa5d" id="u9831aa5d"><br></p><h2 data-lake-id="sDOxa" id="sDOxa"><span data-lake-id="u492a3d02" id="u492a3d02">5. 进阶特性 (v0.3.0+)</span></h2><h3 data-lake-id="rQq8P" id="rQq8P"><span data-lake-id="u5fba0a03" id="u5fba0a03">JSON 原生支持 (v0.7.0)</span></h3><p data-lake-id="u57ae4d1a" id="u57ae4d1a"><span data-lake-id="u93247b69" id="u93247b69">玄铁内置了极简的序列化与反序列化工具。</span></p><ul list="ufbb0c1b4"><li fid="ud3605f50" data-lake-id="u1ddaa3ed" id="u1ddaa3ed"><code data-lake-id="u604c35fc" id="u604c35fc"><span data-lake-id="ufd4cfc73" id="ufd4cfc73">化</span></code><strong><span data-lake-id="ua627604c" id="ua627604c"> (Serialize)</span></strong><span data-lake-id="u9faf5a21" id="u9faf5a21">：将对象转化为 JSON 字符串。</span></li><li fid="ud3605f50" data-lake-id="ua7eb20af" id="ua7eb20af"><code data-lake-id="ube131b33" id="ube131b33"><span data-lake-id="u6b0bf5a7" id="u6b0bf5a7">解</span></code><strong><span data-lake-id="u6ecc5091" id="u6ecc5091"> (Deserialize)</span></strong><span data-lake-id="u59d5f8a1" id="u59d5f8a1">：将 JSON 字符串还原为玄铁对象（字典或数组）。</span></li></ul><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22java%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%E8%AE%BE%20%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%20%3D%20%7B%5C%22%E5%90%8D%5C%22%3A%20%5C%22%E7%8E%84%E9%93%81%5C%22%2C%20%5C%22%E5%80%BC%5C%22%3A%20100%7D%5Cn%E8%AE%BE%20%E6%96%87%E6%9C%AC%20%3D%20%E5%8C%96(%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE)%20%20%2F%2F%20%E5%BE%97%E5%88%B0%20JSON%20%E5%AD%97%E7%AC%A6%E4%B8%B2%5Cn%E8%AE%BE%20%E5%AF%B9%E8%B1%A1%20%3D%20%E8%A7%A3(%E6%96%87%E6%9C%AC)%20%20%2F%2F%20%E8%BF%98%E5%8E%9F%E4%B8%BA%E5%AD%97%E5%85%B8%5Cn%E7%A4%BA(%E5%AF%B9%E8%B1%A1%5B%5C%22%E5%90%8D%5C%22%5D)%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Atrue%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22UsmRk%22%7D"></card><p data-lake-id="u8d10210b" id="u8d10210b"><br></p><p data-lake-id="ub5e524af" id="ub5e524af"><br></p><h3 data-lake-id="Lrwe2" id="Lrwe2"><span data-lake-id="u42bf8844" id="u42bf8844">字典 (Dict)</span></h3><p data-lake-id="u2f8d8f0d" id="u2f8d8f0d"><span data-lake-id="u83ab14c6" id="u83ab14c6">字典使用 </span><code data-lake-id="u9a8b2ab0" id="u9a8b2ab0"><span data-lake-id="u7ecf86d5" id="u7ecf86d5">{键: 值}</span></code><span data-lake-id="ue6f5fc85" id="ue6f5fc85"> 语法。遍历字典时，键的顺序是不确定的。</span></p><ul list="u7960bd5f"><li fid="u856e8a69" data-lake-id="ufa99fa5d" id="ufa99fa5d"><strong><span data-lake-id="u78a89b8b" id="u78a89b8b">键</span></strong><span data-lake-id="ue9c7d9a4" id="ue9c7d9a4">: 目前支持字符串作为键。</span></li><li fid="u856e8a69" data-lake-id="u58dec031" id="u58dec031"><strong><span data-lake-id="u0a6a6a35" id="u0a6a6a35">内置方法</span></strong><span data-lake-id="u96324053" id="u96324053">:</span></li></ul><ul list="u7960bd5f" data-lake-indent="1"><li fid="ud1203848" data-lake-id="u844be754" id="u844be754"><code data-lake-id="uee86027c" id="uee86027c"><span data-lake-id="udb9145d9" id="udb9145d9">d.键()</span></code><span data-lake-id="u4fb71e48" id="u4fb71e48">: 返回所有键的数组。</span></li><li fid="ud1203848" data-lake-id="uae19df02" id="uae19df02"><code data-lake-id="u49004a62" id="u49004a62"><span data-lake-id="ucb197e1a" id="ucb197e1a">d.值()</span></code><span data-lake-id="u5e9e6e63" id="u5e9e6e63">: 返回所有值的数组。</span></li><li fid="ud1203848" data-lake-id="ufb300edd" id="ufb300edd"><code data-lake-id="u74e7deaf" id="u74e7deaf"><span data-lake-id="ufe2c70ff" id="ufe2c70ff">d.含(k)</span></code><span data-lake-id="uca112f18" id="uca112f18"> / </span><code data-lake-id="uf55d1dfc" id="uf55d1dfc"><span data-lake-id="u3a28c4c8" id="u3a28c4c8">d.含?(k)</span></code><span data-lake-id="ud08ad480" id="ud08ad480">: 判断字典是否包含键 </span><code data-lake-id="u23de2b22" id="u23de2b22"><span data-lake-id="u49ddfa5a" id="u49ddfa5a">k</span></code><span data-lake-id="uae2ca636" id="uae2ca636">。</span></li><li fid="ud1203848" data-lake-id="ud8ef12e9" id="ud8ef12e9"><code data-lake-id="u9e99c46d" id="u9e99c46d"><span data-lake-id="u8040deb0" id="u8040deb0">d.空?</span></code><span data-lake-id="ue05475bb" id="ue05475bb"> / </span><code data-lake-id="ud707ccc6" id="ud707ccc6"><span data-lake-id="u91513ec5" id="u91513ec5">d.非空?</span></code><span data-lake-id="uf645b72d" id="uf645b72d">: 判断字典状态。</span></li><li fid="ud1203848" data-lake-id="uec67dc90" id="uec67dc90"><code data-lake-id="u3f7c030f" id="u3f7c030f"><span data-lake-id="u9279f11b" id="u9279f11b">d.删(k)</span></code><span data-lake-id="u67c2f573" id="u67c2f573">: 删除键 </span><code data-lake-id="u4d92144a" id="u4d92144a"><span data-lake-id="ud350d832" id="ud350d832">k</span></code><span data-lake-id="u62740d8f" id="u62740d8f">。</span></li><li fid="ud1203848" data-lake-id="u3446310c" id="u3446310c"><code data-lake-id="ub9640cec" id="ub9640cec"><span data-lake-id="u9368cc87" id="u9368cc87">d.大小</span></code><span data-lake-id="u964e815b" id="u964e815b"> 或 </span><code data-lake-id="u1fa10ec3" id="u1fa10ec3"><span data-lake-id="uccb66a04" id="uccb66a04">d.长度</span></code><span data-lake-id="u16d87cde" id="u16d87cde">: 返回键值对数量。</span></li><li fid="ud1203848" data-lake-id="u90b5e416" id="u90b5e416"><code data-lake-id="ub71b2ba9" id="ub71b2ba9"><span data-lake-id="uea1da5a0" id="uea1da5a0">d.合并(另一字典)</span></code><span data-lake-id="u07b12142" id="u07b12142">: 合并两个字典并返回新字典。</span></li></ul><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22java%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%E8%AE%BE%20%E5%BA%93%20%3D%20%7B%5C%22%E5%90%8D%5C%22%3A%20%5C%22%E7%8E%84%E9%93%81%5C%22%2C%20%5C%22%E5%B2%81%5C%22%3A%201%7D%5Cn%E8%AE%BE%20%E6%96%B0%E5%BA%93%20%3D%20%E5%BA%93.%E5%90%88%E5%B9%B6(%7B%5C%22%E7%89%88%5C%22%3A%200.12%7D)%5Cn%E7%A4%BA(%E6%96%B0%E5%BA%93.%E5%A4%A7%E5%B0%8F)%20%2F%2F%203%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Atrue%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22id%22%3A%22u1DSI%22%7D"></card><p data-lake-id="u03d41a5b" id="u03d41a5b"><br></p><p data-lake-id="u8e5b2080" id="u8e5b2080"><br></p><h3 data-lake-id="FhdXW" id="FhdXW"><span data-lake-id="uacf37aaf" id="uacf37aaf">类与对象</span></h3><p data-lake-id="u404497d0" id="u404497d0"><span data-lake-id="u7924cf1d" id="u7924cf1d">玄铁提供了完整的面向对象编程支持，具备继承、封装、多态及运算符重载能力。</span></p><ul list="u52c65ddc"><li fid="u39d88759" data-lake-id="u51b95f5a" id="u51b95f5a"><code data-lake-id="u2594b684" id="u2594b684"><span data-lake-id="ua336c1d1" id="ua336c1d1">型</span></code><strong><span data-lake-id="u5b73d726" id="u5b73d726"> (Type/Class)</span></strong><span data-lake-id="u815af35d" id="u815af35d">：定义一个数据模型。</span></li><li fid="u39d88759" data-lake-id="u72b417e4" id="u72b417e4"><code data-lake-id="ua97bb7d5" id="ua97bb7d5"><span data-lake-id="ue64b015b" id="ue64b015b">造</span></code><strong><span data-lake-id="u40b831f8" id="u40b831f8"> (New/Construct)</span></strong><span data-lake-id="uf3e68ec0" id="uf3e68ec0">：基于模型创建实例或定义构造函数。</span></li><li fid="u39d88759" data-lake-id="ua305517a" id="ua305517a"><code data-lake-id="u49e35fc3" id="u49e35fc3"><span data-lake-id="uccef1659" id="uccef1659">此</span></code><strong><span data-lake-id="u068719cb" id="u068719cb"> (This/Self)</span></strong><span data-lake-id="ubadbc6d7" id="ubadbc6d7">：在类方法内部引用实例自身及属性。</span></li><li fid="u39d88759" data-lake-id="ub91a7755" id="ub91a7755"><code data-lake-id="ud46e2486" id="ud46e2486"><span data-lake-id="u950fcb00" id="u950fcb00">承</span></code><span data-lake-id="ucf096404" id="ucf096404">** (Inherit)**：实现类之间的继承关系。</span></li><li fid="u39d88759" data-lake-id="u0f05ad6a" id="u0f05ad6a"><code data-lake-id="u3e40d36b" id="u3e40d36b"><span data-lake-id="u1e5c34ac" id="u1e5c34ac">覆</span></code><span data-lake-id="u9284df62" id="u9284df62">** (Override)** (v0.13.0)：重写父类方法时必须显式标注，强化代码契约。</span></li><li fid="u39d88759" data-lake-id="ub2f4d124" id="ub2f4d124"><strong><span data-lake-id="uf369eab3" id="uf369eab3">权限修饰符</span></strong><span data-lake-id="u76c96457" id="u76c96457">：</span></li></ul><ul list="u52c65ddc" data-lake-indent="1"><li fid="u43042487" data-lake-id="uefd662ca" id="uefd662ca"><code data-lake-id="ue3b9e73a" id="ue3b9e73a"><span data-lake-id="u9ecb8afa" id="u9ecb8afa">公</span></code><strong><span data-lake-id="u87e6de25" id="u87e6de25"> (Public)</span></strong><span data-lake-id="u9faebf93" id="u9faebf93">：默认级别，外部可自由读写。</span></li><li fid="u43042487" data-lake-id="ue5640762" id="ue5640762"><code data-lake-id="u313fc113" id="u313fc113"><span data-lake-id="u657693c4" id="u657693c4">私</span></code><span data-lake-id="ue118d1d5" id="ue118d1d5">** (Private)**：仅限本类内部访问，外部和子类均不可见。</span></li><li fid="u43042487" data-lake-id="u0031b50b" id="u0031b50b"><code data-lake-id="ucdcb1aaa" id="ucdcb1aaa"><span data-lake-id="uc893d315" id="uc893d315">护</span></code><span data-lake-id="ud13a2bcf" id="ud13a2bcf">** (Protected)**：受保护级别，允许本类和子类访问，禁止外部直接访问。</span></li></ul><h4 data-lake-id="PJQ6t" id="PJQ6t"><span data-lake-id="ufb219147" id="ufb219147">1. 基础定义与构造</span></h4><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22java%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%E5%9E%8B%20%E5%9D%90%E6%A0%87%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20%E8%AE%BE%20x%20%3D%200%5Cn%20%20%20%20%E7%A7%81%20%E8%AE%BE%20y%20%3D%200%5Cn%5Cn%20%20%20%20%2F%2F%20%E6%9E%84%E9%80%A0%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%5Cn%20%20%20%20%E5%87%BD%20%E9%80%A0(%E5%88%9D%E5%A7%8Bx%2C%20%E5%88%9D%E5%A7%8By)%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%E6%AD%A4.x%20%3D%20%E5%88%9D%E5%A7%8Bx%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%E6%AD%A4.y%20%3D%20%E5%88%9D%E5%A7%8By%5Cn%20%20%20%20%7D%5Cn%7D%5Cn%E8%AE%BE%20%E7%82%B9%20%3D%20%E9%80%A0%20%E5%9D%90%E6%A0%87(10%2C%2020)%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Atrue%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22id%22%3A%22BgC38%22%7D"></card><h4 data-lake-id="hEtc7" id="hEtc7"><span data-lake-id="u90589ba1" id="u90589ba1">2. 继承 (承) 与 保护 (护)</span></h4><p data-lake-id="u99de6244" id="u99de6244"><code data-lake-id="u40d505bc" id="u40d505bc"><span data-lake-id="ue52f3775" id="ue52f3775">承</span></code><span data-lake-id="u8842f135" id="u8842f135"> 实现了代码复用，而 </span><code data-lake-id="u69a971a4" id="u69a971a4"><span data-lake-id="ucef7c535" id="ucef7c535">护</span></code><span data-lake-id="u22fa9b2b" id="u22fa9b2b"> 确保了敏感逻辑在“家族链”内部的安全流动。</span></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22java%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%E5%9E%8B%20%E8%B4%A6%E6%88%B7%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20%E5%85%AC%20%E8%AE%BE%20%E6%88%B7%E5%90%8D%20%3D%20%5C%22%E8%AE%BF%E5%AE%A2%5C%22%5Cn%20%20%20%20%E6%8A%A4%20%E8%AE%BE%20%E4%BD%99%E9%A2%9D%20%3D%200%20%20%2F%2F%20%E5%8F%AA%E6%9C%89%E5%AE%B6%E6%97%8F%E6%88%90%E5%91%98%EF%BC%88%E5%AD%90%E7%B1%BB%EF%BC%89%E8%83%BD%E5%8A%A8%E4%BD%99%E9%A2%9D%5Cn%20%20%20%20%E7%A7%81%20%E8%AE%BE%20%E5%86%85%E9%83%A8%E6%A0%87%E8%AE%B0%20%3D%20%5C%22SECRET%5C%22%20%2F%2F%20%E5%8F%AA%E6%9C%89%E8%B4%A6%E6%88%B7%E7%B1%BB%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E8%83%BD%E7%9C%8B%5Cn%7D%5Cn%5Cn%E5%9E%8B%20%E4%BF%A1%E7%94%A8%E5%8D%A1%20%E6%89%BF%20%E8%B4%A6%E6%88%B7%20%7B%20%20%2F%2F%20%E4%BF%A1%E7%94%A8%E5%8D%A1%20%E7%BB%A7%E6%89%BF%E4%BA%86%20%E8%B4%A6%E6%88%B7%5Cn%20%20%20%20%E5%87%BD%20%E5%AD%98%E6%AC%BE(%E6%95%B0%E9%A2%9D)%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%E4%BD%99%E9%A2%9D%20%3D%20%E4%BD%99%E9%A2%9D%20%2B%20%E6%95%B0%E9%A2%9D%20%2F%2F%20%E5%90%88%E6%B3%95%EF%BC%9A%E5%AD%90%E7%B1%BB%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E8%AE%BF%E9%97%AE%E2%80%9C%E6%8A%A4%E2%80%9D%E5%B1%9E%E6%80%A7%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%E7%A4%BA(%5C%22%E5%AD%98%E5%85%A5%E6%88%90%E5%8A%9F%EF%BC%8C%E5%BD%93%E5%89%8D%E4%BD%99%E9%A2%9D%3A%20%5C%22%20%26%20%E4%BD%99%E9%A2%9D)%5Cn%20%20%20%20%7D%5Cn%7D%5Cn%5Cn%E8%AE%BE%20%E6%88%91%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%A1%20%3D%20%E9%80%A0%20%E4%BF%A1%E7%94%A8%E5%8D%A1()%5Cn%E6%88%91%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%A1.%E5%AD%98%E6%AC%BE(1000)%5Cn%E7%A4%BA(%E6%88%91%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%A1.%E6%88%B7%E5%90%8D)%20%20%20%2F%2F%20%E5%90%88%E6%B3%95%EF%BC%9A%E5%85%AC%E6%9C%89%E5%B1%9E%E6%80%A7%5Cn%2F%2F%20%E7%A4%BA(%E6%88%91%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%A1.%E4%BD%99%E9%A2%9D)%20%2F%2F%20%E6%8A%A5%E9%94%99%EF%BC%9A%E5%A4%96%E9%83%A8%E7%A6%81%E6%AD%A2%E8%AE%BF%E9%97%AE%E5%8F%97%E4%BF%9D%E6%8A%A4%E5%B1%9E%E6%80%A7%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Atrue%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22CoxD0%22%7D"></card><h4 data-lake-id="Afzh2" id="Afzh2"><span data-lake-id="u189c28f5" id="u189c28f5">3. 继承 (承) 与 重写 (覆)</span></h4><p data-lake-id="ufa0ad49c" id="ufa0ad49c"><span data-lake-id="ub202204c" id="ub202204c">子类重写父类方法时，必须使用 </span><code data-lake-id="u6d91e79c" id="u6d91e79c"><span data-lake-id="u3baf189a" id="u3baf189a">覆</span></code><span data-lake-id="u14c6c324" id="u14c6c324"> 关键字，这能有效防止因拼写错误导致的意外“重写”失败。</span></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22java%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%E5%9E%8B%20%E5%8A%A8%E7%89%A9%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20%E5%87%BD%20%E5%8F%AB()%20%7B%20%E7%A4%BA(%5C%22%E5%8A%A8%E7%89%A9%E5%8F%AB%5C%22)%20%7D%5Cn%7D%5Cn%5Cn%E5%9E%8B%20%E7%8C%AB%20%E6%89%BF%20%E5%8A%A8%E7%89%A9%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20%E8%A6%86%20%E5%87%BD%20%E5%8F%AB()%20%7B%20%E7%A4%BA(%5C%22%E5%96%B5%E5%96%B5%E5%96%B5~%5C%22)%20%7D%5Cn%7D%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Atrue%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22LMciD%22%7D"></card><h4 data-lake-id="mvq9X" id="mvq9X"><span data-lake-id="u4813b003" id="u4813b003">4. 运算符重载 (v0.13.0)</span></h4><p data-lake-id="ua9529df0" id="ua9529df0"><span data-lake-id="u217efba8" id="u217efba8">玄铁支持通过定义“魔术方法”来重载自定义类型的运算符行为：</span></p><ul list="u5803b6da"><li fid="ua139336b" data-lake-id="uf5de5b3a" id="uf5de5b3a"><code data-lake-id="u6c0c6b5d" id="u6c0c6b5d"><span data-lake-id="ucd157365" id="ucd157365">_加_(另)</span></code><span data-lake-id="uc2f8d91d" id="uc2f8d91d">：对应 </span><code data-lake-id="uc483fa88" id="uc483fa88"><span data-lake-id="ub53ed882" id="ub53ed882">+</span></code></li><li fid="ua139336b" data-lake-id="u167057ac" id="u167057ac"><code data-lake-id="udd183692" id="udd183692"><span data-lake-id="ucd51871b" id="ucd51871b">_减_(另)</span></code><span data-lake-id="ua6ead4b5" id="ua6ead4b5">：对应 </span><code data-lake-id="u93cb802d" id="u93cb802d"><span data-lake-id="u285c2e92" id="u285c2e92">-</span></code></li><li fid="ua139336b" data-lake-id="u904e5c3d" id="u904e5c3d"><code data-lake-id="u8bab592b" id="u8bab592b"><span data-lake-id="u0a0cbee9" id="u0a0cbee9">_乘_(另)</span></code><span data-lake-id="ud67c78ba" id="ud67c78ba">：对应 </span><code data-lake-id="u4f084c36" id="u4f084c36"><span data-lake-id="uefb0d099" id="uefb0d099">*</span></code></li><li fid="ua139336b" data-lake-id="u197a8046" id="u197a8046"><code data-lake-id="u35062f8f" id="u35062f8f"><span data-lake-id="u2fcf1f1e" id="u2fcf1f1e">_除_(另)</span></code><span data-lake-id="u745e8f1e" id="u745e8f1e">：对应 </span><code data-lake-id="u4361cf9e" id="u4361cf9e"><span data-lake-id="u342fe64b" id="u342fe64b">/</span></code></li><li fid="ua139336b" data-lake-id="u6b157ffb" id="u6b157ffb"><code data-lake-id="uf61b8d0b" id="uf61b8d0b"><span data-lake-id="u16fe22f6" id="u16fe22f6">_等_(另)</span></code><span data-lake-id="uda39644d" id="uda39644d">：对应 </span><code data-lake-id="u77f281f8" id="u77f281f8"><span data-lake-id="uff6482fb" id="uff6482fb">==</span></code></li></ul><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22java%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%E5%9E%8B%20%E5%90%91%E9%87%8F%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20%E8%AE%BE%20x%3B%20%E8%AE%BE%20y%5Cn%20%20%20%20%E5%87%BD%20%E9%80%A0(x%2C%20y)%20%7B%20%E6%AD%A4.x%20%3D%20x%3B%20%E6%AD%A4.y%20%3D%20y%20%7D%5Cn%20%20%20%20%5Cn%20%20%20%20%E5%87%BD%20_%E5%8A%A0_(%E5%8F%A6)%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%E8%BF%94%20%E9%80%A0%20%E5%90%91%E9%87%8F(%E6%AD%A4.x%20%2B%20%E5%8F%A6.x%2C%20%E6%AD%A4.y%20%2B%20%E5%8F%A6.y)%5Cn%20%20%20%20%7D%5Cn%7D%5Cn%5Cn%E8%AE%BE%20v1%20%3D%20%E9%80%A0%20%E5%90%91%E9%87%8F(1%2C%202)%5Cn%E8%AE%BE%20v2%20%3D%20%E9%80%A0%20%E5%90%91%E9%87%8F(3%2C%204)%5Cn%E8%AE%BE%20v3%20%3D%20v1%20%2B%20v2%20%2F%2F%20%E8%87%AA%E5%8A%A8%E8%B0%83%E7%94%A8%20_%E5%8A%A0_%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Atrue%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22U4oOK%22%7D"></card><p data-lake-id="u0a1f0164" id="u0a1f0164"><br></p><p data-lake-id="u570cbd41" id="u570cbd41"><br></p><h3 data-lake-id="yMYye" id="yMYye"><span data-lake-id="u217b8963" id="u217b8963">网络与系统原语 (v0.9.0)</span></h3><p data-lake-id="ud2b5f2e2" id="ud2b5f2e2"><span data-lake-id="u8bbd5e7b" id="u8bbd5e7b">玄铁通过极简的单字原语，将复杂的网络通讯和系统交互降维到“管道读写”级别。</span></p><h4 data-lake-id="UTdkU" id="UTdkU"><span data-lake-id="uc24fe9fd" id="uc24fe9fd">1. 网络请求 (</span><code data-lake-id="u15e59885" id="u15e59885"><span data-lake-id="u20990827" id="u20990827">求</span></code><span data-lake-id="u671692c5" id="u671692c5">)</span></h4><p data-lake-id="u7070b316" id="u7070b316"><span data-lake-id="u6768c8c3" id="u6768c8c3">一行代码获取互联网数据，原生返回 </span><code data-lake-id="u0b7d6b7b" id="u0b7d6b7b"><span data-lake-id="ud8bcfdd3" id="ud8bcfdd3">结果</span></code><span data-lake-id="u7e658eb4" id="u7e658eb4"> 容器。</span></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22java%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%E6%B1%82(%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapi.github.com%5C%22).%E6%8E%A5%E7%9D%80(%E5%87%BD(%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9)%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20%E7%A4%BA(%5C%22%E6%94%B6%E5%88%B0%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%3A%20%5C%22%20%26%20%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9)%5Cn%7D)%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Atrue%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22Zwga6%22%7D"></card><h4 data-lake-id="GWY0U" id="GWY0U"><span data-lake-id="udfc27b33" id="udfc27b33">2. Socket 与 HTTP 通讯 (</span><code data-lake-id="uc33336a4" id="uc33336a4"><span data-lake-id="ufb14cd52" id="ufb14cd52">听</span></code><span data-lake-id="uf6874fde" id="uf6874fde"> 与 </span><code data-lake-id="u58baa574" id="u58baa574"><span data-lake-id="ucab6c9e3" id="ucab6c9e3">连</span></code><span data-lake-id="u66aba567" id="u66aba567">)</span></h4><p data-lake-id="u3cf40472" id="u3cf40472"><span data-lake-id="u17e0d8da" id="u17e0d8da">玄铁的 </span><code data-lake-id="u38cfca00" id="u38cfca00"><span data-lake-id="u97b826e9" id="u97b826e9">听</span></code><span data-lake-id="u39131089" id="u39131089"> 关键字具有多态性，能根据回调函数的参数数量自动切换 TCP 或 HTTP 模式。</span></p><ul list="uffce4dcd"><li fid="u886f8ce0" data-lake-id="ucc7a4f43" id="ucc7a4f43"><strong><span data-lake-id="u3337406f" id="u3337406f">TCP 模式</span></strong><span data-lake-id="uca9b3df6" id="uca9b3df6">：回调函数接收 1 个参数 (</span><code data-lake-id="u9dff01f6" id="u9dff01f6"><span data-lake-id="ude9a4708" id="ude9a4708">流</span></code><span data-lake-id="u5f581b39" id="u5f581b39">)。</span></li></ul><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22java%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%E5%90%AC(9000%2C%20%E5%87%BD(%E7%AE%A1%E9%81%93)%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20%E8%AE%BE%20%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%20%3D%20%E7%AE%A1%E9%81%93.%E8%AF%BB()%5Cn%20%20%20%20%E7%AE%A1%E9%81%93.%E5%86%99(%5C%22%E5%B7%B2%E6%94%B6%E5%88%B0%5C%22)%5Cn%20%20%20%20%E7%AE%A1%E9%81%93.%E5%85%B3()%5Cn%7D)%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Atrue%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22FtkVO%22%7D"></card><ul list="ub63ba5a3"><li fid="uc1b278b0" data-lake-id="u6e9b6909" id="u6e9b6909"><strong><span data-lake-id="u928e33ae" id="u928e33ae">HTTP 模式</span></strong><span data-lake-id="u0b7e6549" id="u0b7e6549">：回调函数接收 2 个参数 (</span><code data-lake-id="ufc8a8400" id="ufc8a8400"><span data-lake-id="u5c9711bf" id="u5c9711bf">请</span></code><span data-lake-id="udcd559d7" id="udcd559d7">, </span><code data-lake-id="u95e53dbf" id="u95e53dbf"><span data-lake-id="u859429aa" id="u859429aa">答</span></code><span data-lake-id="uc32366af" id="uc32366af">)。</span></li></ul><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22java%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%E5%90%AC(8080%2C%20%E5%87%BD(%E8%AF%B7%2C%20%E7%AD%94)%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20%E7%A4%BA(%5C%22%E6%94%B6%E5%88%B0%E8%AF%B7%E6%B1%82%3A%20%5C%22%20%26%20%E8%AF%B7%5B%5C%22%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%5C%22%5D%20%26%20%5C%22%20%5C%22%20%26%20%E8%AF%B7%5B%5C%22%E8%B7%AF%E5%BE%84%5C%22%5D)%5Cn%20%20%20%20%E7%AD%94.%E5%A4%B4(%5C%22Content-Type%5C%22%2C%20%5C%22text%2Fplain%5C%22)%5Cn%20%20%20%20%E7%AD%94.%E7%A0%81(200)%5Cn%20%20%20%20%E7%AD%94.%E5%86%99(%5C%22%E4%BD%A0%E5%A5%BD%EF%BC%8C%E7%8E%84%E9%93%81%20HTTP%5C%22)%5Cn%7D)%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Atrue%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22sXt14%22%7D"></card><ul list="ua3f96957"><li fid="u75544bb9" data-lake-id="u70157d00" id="u70157d00"><code data-lake-id="uac54841c" id="uac54841c"><span data-lake-id="u741a764f" id="u741a764f">连</span></code><strong><span data-lake-id="udfe87474" id="udfe87474"> (Connect)</span></strong><span data-lake-id="u59f2ee60" id="u59f2ee60">：建立 TCP 客户端连接，返回 </span><code data-lake-id="u87583ca3" id="u87583ca3"><span data-lake-id="u87bf1492" id="u87bf1492">结果(流)</span></code><span data-lake-id="ua51609ee" id="ua51609ee">。</span></li><li fid="u75544bb9" data-lake-id="u2d1b5903" id="u2d1b5903"><code data-lake-id="u7d257a91" id="u7d257a91"><span data-lake-id="uae7b5d86" id="uae7b5d86">道</span></code><strong><span data-lake-id="ueb2fc99f" id="ueb2fc99f"> (Channel)</span></strong><span data-lake-id="u93b0b358" id="u93b0b358"> (v0.9.0)：创建并发通讯通道。</span></li></ul><ul list="ua3f96957" data-lake-indent="1"><li fid="u4c4f58e8" data-lake-id="u76ca5ec4" id="u76ca5ec4"><code data-lake-id="u34370031" id="u34370031"><span data-lake-id="ub7aa4dfb" id="ub7aa4dfb">设 通 = 道</span></code><span data-lake-id="u1ae62b85" id="u1ae62b85">：创建默认通道（缓冲大小 100）。</span></li><li fid="u4c4f58e8" data-lake-id="u764eb6f9" id="u764eb6f9"><code data-lake-id="u8f389346" id="u8f389346"><span data-lake-id="u69dc9175" id="u69dc9175">通.发(值)</span></code><span data-lake-id="u33ed35a4" id="u33ed35a4">：向通道发送数据。</span></li><li fid="u4c4f58e8" data-lake-id="u02171761" id="u02171761"><code data-lake-id="u4a251bfe" id="u4a251bfe"><span data-lake-id="u7a938c4d" id="u7a938c4d">通.收()</span></code><span data-lake-id="uaed09703" id="uaed09703">：从通道接收数据（阻塞）。</span></li><li fid="u4c4f58e8" data-lake-id="u065a7c53" id="u065a7c53"><code data-lake-id="u89939e7a" id="u89939e7a"><span data-lake-id="ue7c1e4cd" id="ue7c1e4cd">通.关()</span></code><span data-lake-id="u968afb1c" id="u968afb1c">：关闭通道。</span></li></ul><ul list="ua3f96957" start="3"><li fid="u75544bb9" data-lake-id="u6d2c3960" id="u6d2c3960"><code data-lake-id="ub148a82a" id="ub148a82a"><span data-lake-id="u685212f2" id="u685212f2">流</span></code><strong><span data-lake-id="u2b3b6485" id="u2b3b6485"> (Stream)</span></strong><span data-lake-id="u03ce1dd1" id="u03ce1dd1">：支持 </span><code data-lake-id="u229a5e0c" id="u229a5e0c"><span data-lake-id="u54bf0f79" id="u54bf0f79">读</span></code><span data-lake-id="u6725a0f8" id="u6725a0f8">、</span><code data-lake-id="ucdc4145b" id="ucdc4145b"><span data-lake-id="uc2cf0a67" id="uc2cf0a67">写</span></code><span data-lake-id="u92a98027" id="u92a98027">、</span><code data-lake-id="uaf99b604" id="uaf99b604"><span data-lake-id="u21213a43" id="u21213a43">关</span></code><span data-lake-id="udd3e7a4d" id="udd3e7a4d"> 操作。</span></li></ul><h4 data-lake-id="ZSugK" id="ZSugK"><span data-lake-id="u747c183b" id="u747c183b">3. 系统执行 (</span><code data-lake-id="u1dc918e2" id="u1dc918e2"><span data-lake-id="u0efe0e4a" id="u0efe0e4a">执</span></code><span data-lake-id="uaa4e5760" id="uaa4e5760">)</span></h4><p data-lake-id="ucebe25a0" id="ucebe25a0"><span data-lake-id="ub83a68a3" id="ub83a68a3">调用操作系统命令，并获取其输出。</span></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22java%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%E6%89%A7(%5C%22git%20status%5C%22).%E6%8E%A5%E7%9D%80(%E5%87%BD(%E8%BE%93%E5%87%BA)%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20%E7%A4%BA(%E8%BE%93%E5%87%BA)%5Cn%7D)%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Atrue%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22VtKGo%22%7D"></card><h4 data-lake-id="s0dUO" id="s0dUO"><span data-lake-id="ub201fc93" id="ub201fc93">4. 通道通讯 (</span><code data-lake-id="u7a8de2f0" id="u7a8de2f0"><span data-lake-id="ueb8d21e5" id="ueb8d21e5">道</span></code><span data-lake-id="uba6d94af" id="uba6d94af">)</span></h4><p data-lake-id="u1445d1e5" id="u1445d1e5"><span data-lake-id="ufcb32365" id="ufcb32365">在不同的异步任务（协程）之间安全地传递数据。</span></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22java%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%E8%AE%BE%20%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF%E9%81%93%20%3D%20%E9%81%93%5Cn%E5%BC%82%E6%AD%A5%20%7B%20%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF%E9%81%93.%E9%80%81(%5C%22%E7%A7%98%E5%AF%86%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%5C%22)%20%7D%5Cn%E8%AE%BE%20%E6%94%B6%E5%88%B0%20%3D%20%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF%E9%81%93.%E6%94%B6()%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Atrue%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22F7YWr%22%7D"></card><p data-lake-id="u05831720" id="u05831720"><br></p><p data-lake-id="u72112bb5" id="u72112bb5"><br></p><h3 data-lake-id="P0BBg" id="P0BBg"><span data-lake-id="u35191c17" id="u35191c17">字节处理 (字节) (v0.9.2)</span></h3><p data-lake-id="u6920bc10" id="u6920bc10"><span data-lake-id="u3cf506b5" id="u3cf506b5">用于处理二进制数据，支持与字符串互转。</span></p><ul list="uf47fc502"><li fid="udc6390f9" data-lake-id="u9b1b156b" id="u9b1b156b"><code data-lake-id="u0dfe58eb" id="u0dfe58eb"><span data-lake-id="u290681bb" id="u290681bb" style="color: #117CEE">字节</span><span data-lake-id="u93f58a0e" id="u93f58a0e">.</span><span data-lake-id="ue41fd392" id="ue41fd392" style="color: #ED740C">从字</span><span data-lake-id="u956c0dc9" id="u956c0dc9">(s)</span></code><span data-lake-id="uff10f9b9" id="uff10f9b9">: 将字符串转为字节数组。</span></li><li fid="udc6390f9" data-lake-id="u634fb136" id="u634fb136"><code data-lake-id="u2485db87" id="u2485db87"><span data-lake-id="u1b32ac38" id="u1b32ac38" style="color: #117CEE">字节</span><span data-lake-id="ud909580a" id="ud909580a">.</span><span data-lake-id="u0fb40825" id="u0fb40825" style="color: #ED740C">到字</span><span data-lake-id="u9b8e2276" id="u9b8e2276">(b)</span></code><span data-lake-id="u5fdff3fe" id="u5fdff3fe">: 将字节数组转为字符串。</span></li><li fid="udc6390f9" data-lake-id="u0420ac7e" id="u0420ac7e"><span data-lake-id="u139827c5" id="u139827c5">属性 </span><code data-lake-id="u36de5669" id="u36de5669"><span data-lake-id="u63125db3" id="u63125db3">.</span><span data-lake-id="ub47178fe" id="ub47178fe" style="color: #ED740C">长度</span></code><span data-lake-id="u184916c7" id="u184916c7">: 获取字节数。</span></li><li fid="udc6390f9" data-lake-id="uc97bfe9d" id="uc97bfe9d"><span data-lake-id="ud194e4bc" id="ud194e4bc">索引 </span><code data-lake-id="u79bcf681" id="u79bcf681"><span data-lake-id="u087bf406" id="u087bf406">[i]</span></code><span data-lake-id="ub811ebd2" id="ub811ebd2">: 获取指定位置的字节值 (0-255)。</span></li></ul><h3 data-lake-id="cEH6h" id="cEH6h"><span data-lake-id="u7ed63c90" id="u7ed63c90">系统权能 (系统) (v0.9.2)</span></h3><ul list="u3b54bd22"><li fid="u8f91f775" data-lake-id="u0b9fafe6" id="u0b9fafe6"><code data-lake-id="uba83d039" id="uba83d039"><span data-lake-id="uddbaa99f" id="uddbaa99f" style="color: #117CEE">系统</span><span data-lake-id="u0a417c3f" id="u0a417c3f">.</span><span data-lake-id="u53181f4c" id="u53181f4c" style="color: #ED740C">参数</span></code><span data-lake-id="uad2beee1" id="uad2beee1">: 返回一个字符串数组，包含程序启动时的所有命令行参数。</span></li></ul><h3 data-lake-id="rINsU" id="rINsU"><span data-lake-id="u16fcbdd6" id="u16fcbdd6">外部函数接口 (外) (v0.9.1)</span></h3><p data-lake-id="ucf79006c" id="ucf79006c"><span data-lake-id="u91faee7d" id="u91faee7d">玄铁支持直接调用 C 语言编写的动态库（Windows </span><code data-lake-id="u2229fbc6" id="u2229fbc6"><span data-lake-id="u0dbbc7c8" id="u0dbbc7c8">.dll</span></code><span data-lake-id="ue460d76d" id="ue460d76d"> 或 Linux </span><code data-lake-id="u464adb03" id="u464adb03"><span data-lake-id="u43a137b1" id="u43a137b1">.so</span></code><span data-lake-id="ue507c6e6" id="ue507c6e6">）。玄铁会自动识别以 </span><code data-lake-id="u10a45b8f" id="u10a45b8f"><span data-lake-id="u86e518de" id="u86e518de">W</span></code><span data-lake-id="u4c3e90c6" id="u4c3e90c6"> 结尾的 Windows 函数并使用 UTF-16 编码，彻底解决乱码问题。</span></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22java%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%E5%A4%96.%E5%8A%A0%E8%BD%BD(%5C%22user32.dll%5C%22).%E6%8E%A5%E7%9D%80(%E5%87%BD(%E5%BA%93)%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20%2F%2F%20%E8%B0%83%E7%94%A8%20MessageBoxW%20(Unicode%E7%89%88%E6%9C%AC)%5Cn%20%20%20%20%E8%AE%BE%20%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%9C%20%3D%20%E5%BA%93.MessageBoxW(0%2C%20%5C%22%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9%5C%22%2C%20%5C%22%E6%A0%87%E9%A2%98%5C%22%2C%200)%5Cn%20%20%20%20%E7%A4%BA(%5C%22%E8%BF%94%E5%9B%9E%3A%20%5C%22%20%26%20%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%9C)%5Cn%7D)%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Atrue%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22Bq5i7%22%7D"></card><h3 data-lake-id="YIFg0" id="YIFg0"><span data-lake-id="u4f089a03" id="u4f089a03">交叉编译</span></h3><p data-lake-id="uc07da2e2" id="uc07da2e2"><span data-lake-id="u47ea4fe0" id="u47ea4fe0">玄铁命令行支持一键构建跨平台程序。</span></p><blockquote data-lake-id="ubabc1bcf" id="ubabc1bcf"><p data-lake-id="u3d15ab0a" id="u3d15ab0a"><span data-lake-id="u94f4bd0f" id="u94f4bd0f">zao=造=编译 | pt=pingtai=平台 | jg=jiagou=架构</span></p></blockquote><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22java%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%23%20%E5%9C%A8%20Windows%20%E4%B8%8B%E7%BC%96%E8%AF%91%20Linux%20%E7%89%88%E6%9C%AC%5Cnxuantie%20zao%20%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%8F.xt%20--pt%20linux%20--jg%20amd64%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Atrue%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22Lfmdu%22%7D"></card><h3 data-lake-id="bGzrb" id="bGzrb"><span data-lake-id="u1df85466" id="u1df85466">结果处理 (Result)</span></h3><p data-lake-id="ucd7fea44" id="ucd7fea44"><span data-lake-id="u15160edc" id="u15160edc">引入函数式错误处理，避免嵌套的 </span><code data-lake-id="ua1b72813" id="ua1b72813"><span data-lake-id="u4f426d7b" id="u4f426d7b">if err != nil</span></code><span data-lake-id="u4484d6d5" id="u4484d6d5">。</span></p><blockquote data-lake-id="uf655af87" id="uf655af87"><p data-lake-id="u3504186f" id="u3504186f"><span data-lake-id="uadd5b67e" id="uadd5b67e">这种写法主要参照了 JavaScript (Promises) 、 Rust ( </span><code data-lake-id="ufa1d7ace" id="ufa1d7ace"><span data-lake-id="u4ee075e3" id="u4ee075e3">Result&lt;T, E&gt;</span></code><span data-lake-id="u96a8ef91" id="u96a8ef91"> )</span></p></blockquote><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22java%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%E8%AE%BE%20%E8%8E%B7%E5%8F%96%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%20%3D%20%E5%87%BD()%20%7B%20%E8%BF%94%20%E6%88%90%E5%8A%9F(%5C%22%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%5C%22)%20%7D%5Cn%5Cn%E8%8E%B7%E5%8F%96%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE()%5Cn.%E6%8E%A5%E7%9D%80(%E5%87%BD(%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9)%20%7B%20%E7%A4%BA(%5C%22%E6%88%90%E5%8A%9F%3A%20%5C%22%20%26%20%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9)%20%7D)%5Cn.%E5%90%A6%E5%88%99(%E5%87%BD(%E9%94%99%E8%AF%AF)%20%7B%20%E7%A4%BA(%5C%22%E5%A4%B1%E8%B4%A5%3A%20%5C%22%20%26%20%E9%94%99%E8%AF%AF)%20%7D)%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Atrue%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22id%22%3A%22tIBIY%22%7D"></card><p data-lake-id="ub6891623" id="ub6891623"><span data-lake-id="u1ca2108c" id="u1ca2108c">相比传统，如</span><strong><span data-lake-id="udffefa03" id="udffefa03">C语言</span></strong><span data-lake-id="u8d819708" id="u8d819708">的示例写法：</span></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22c%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%2F%2F%20C%20%E8%AF%AD%E8%A8%80%E9%A3%8E%E6%A0%BC%EF%BC%9A%E4%B8%8D%E6%96%AD%E5%9C%B0%E6%A3%80%E6%9F%A5%E8%BF%94%E5%9B%9E%E7%8A%B6%E6%80%81%5Cnint%20err%20%3D%20get_data(%26data)%3B%5Cnif%20(err%20%3D%3D%20SUCCESS)%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20int%20err2%20%3D%20process_data(data%2C%20%26result)%3B%5Cn%20%20%20%20if%20(err2%20%3D%3D%20SUCCESS)%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20save(result)%3B%5Cn%20%20%20%20%7D%20else%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20%20%20%20%20handle_error(err2)%3B%5Cn%20%20%20%20%7D%5Cn%7D%20else%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20handle_error(err)%3B%5Cn%7D%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Atrue%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22n9a1q%22%7D"></card><p data-lake-id="u78858936" id="u78858936"><span data-lake-id="uf00c5079" id="uf00c5079">这种写法会导致著名的</span><strong><span data-lake-id="u3bdfeed1" id="u3bdfeed1">“金字塔嵌套”</span></strong><span data-lake-id="ua70c6459" id="ua70c6459">或大量的 </span><code data-lake-id="ub37ee4e5" id="ub37ee4e5"><span data-lake-id="ucbd91e51" id="ucbd91e51">if (err != 0) goto cleanup</span></code><span data-lake-id="u9e3f59fb" id="u9e3f59fb"> 。</span></p><h4 data-lake-id="T0m40" id="T0m40"><span data-lake-id="ucb6c01c7" id="ucb6c01c7">玄铁的解决方案是“管道化”</span></h4><ul list="ud7132bac"><li fid="u0e4ed2c3" data-lake-id="u602581cf" id="u602581cf"><code data-lake-id="u74b24ce7" id="u74b24ce7"><span data-lake-id="u8595b605" id="u8595b605">.接着</span></code><span data-lake-id="u38114ec8" id="u38114ec8">的本质： </span><code data-lake-id="ub7159c82" id="ub7159c82"><span data-lake-id="u190a252e" id="u190a252e">获取数据()</span></code><span data-lake-id="u0edff54b" id="u0edff54b"> 返回的不是一个简单的整数或指针，而是一个 结果 (Result) 容器。这个容器像一个包裹，里面可能装着“成功的数据”，也可能装着“失败的错误”。</span></li><li fid="u0e4ed2c3" data-lake-id="u30c42811" id="u30c42811"><span data-lake-id="ue9da5f1e" id="ue9da5f1e">链式调用 ： </span><code data-lake-id="uc7e1d860" id="uc7e1d860"><span data-lake-id="u44b41696" id="u44b41696">.接着</span></code><span data-lake-id="u740bf0d1" id="u740bf0d1"> 是这个容器的一个方法。它的逻辑是：“如果你（容器）里面是成功的，就请执行我传给你的函数；如果你是失败的，请跳过我，把错误直接传给下一个人。”</span></li><li fid="u0e4ed2c3" data-lake-id="ubf4111fc" id="ubf4111fc"><span data-lake-id="uaa0863bf" id="uaa0863bf">换行与点 ：这是一种 视觉对齐 。它让代码读起来像一个 流水线清单 ：</span></li></ul><ol list="uf87f013c" data-lake-indent="1"><li fid="u339c9a9a" data-lake-id="uc85d20ac" id="uc85d20ac"><span data-lake-id="ud8a6698d" id="ud8a6698d">获取数据</span></li><li fid="u339c9a9a" data-lake-id="u387b3b84" id="u387b3b84"><code data-lake-id="ua0d38adf" id="ua0d38adf"><span data-lake-id="ub05a67d2" id="ub05a67d2">.接着</span></code><span data-lake-id="uaffd9c2a" id="uaffd9c2a"> 处理它</span></li><li fid="u339c9a9a" data-lake-id="u4895768a" id="u4895768a"><code data-lake-id="u41e3f5a3" id="u41e3f5a3"><span data-lake-id="ue4ae1b3b" id="ue4ae1b3b">.接着</span></code><span data-lake-id="ufed99419" id="ufed99419"> 转换它</span></li><li fid="u339c9a9a" data-lake-id="u5503aaa3" id="u5503aaa3"><code data-lake-id="u7744dc2d" id="u7744dc2d"><span data-lake-id="uacb8be2a" id="uacb8be2a">.否则</span></code><span data-lake-id="u46406301" id="u46406301"> 报错</span></li></ol><h3 data-lake-id="Sux0q" id="Sux0q"><span data-lake-id="uefb78a3f" id="uefb78a3f">异步与并行 (Async/Parallel)</span></h3><p data-lake-id="ub16dd153" id="ub16dd153"><span data-lake-id="u8681f584" id="u8681f584">原生支持并发，底层基于 Go 协程。</span></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22java%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%2F%2F%20%E5%BC%82%E6%AD%A5%E6%89%A7%E8%A1%8C%5Cn%E8%AE%BE%20%E4%BB%BB%E5%8A%A1%20%3D%20%E5%BC%82%E6%AD%A5%20%7B%20%E8%80%97%E6%97%B6%E4%BB%BB%E5%8A%A1()%20%7D%5Cn%E8%AE%BE%20%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%9C%20%3D%20%E7%AD%89%E5%BE%85(%E4%BB%BB%E5%8A%A1)%5Cn%5Cn%2F%2F%20%E5%B9%B6%E8%A1%8C%E6%89%A7%E8%A1%8C%E5%A4%9A%E4%B8%AA%E5%9D%97%5Cn%E8%AE%BE%20%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%9C%E9%9B%86%20%3D%20%E5%B9%B6%E8%A1%8C%20%7B%5Cn%7B%20%E4%BB%BB%E5%8A%A11()%20%7D%2C%5Cn%7B%20%E4%BB%BB%E5%8A%A12()%20%7D%5Cn%7D%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Atrue%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22id%22%3A%22AdiDu%22%7D"></card><details data-lake-id="udd169487" id="udd169487" open="true" class="lake-collapse"><summary data-lake-id="ub7b3f4bb" id="ub7b3f4bb" class="lake-summary"><span data-lake-id="ud62fea67" id="ud62fea67">异步与并行的原理</span></summary><h4 data-lake-id="OQwY4" id="OQwY4"><span data-lake-id="u74afe716" id="u74afe716">异步与并行的原理：从“管理线程”到“管理任务”</span></h4><h5 data-lake-id="SmdQ1" id="SmdQ1" data-lake-index-type="0"><span data-lake-id="u45534575" id="u45534575">底层原理 (M:N 调度)</span></h5><p data-lake-id="ua1d473c0" id="ua1d473c0"><span data-lake-id="u1d1d62ee" id="u1d1d62ee">玄铁的异步底层完全继承了 Go 语言的 协程 (Goroutine) 和 调度器 (Scheduler) 机制。</span></p><ul list="u56daa7bd"><li fid="u3d074b21" data-lake-id="u037a9b18" id="u037a9b18"><span data-lake-id="u742bcaca" id="u742bcaca">传统语言 (C/C++/Java) ：通常是 1:1 线程模型。开启一个异步任务意味着向操作系统申请一个内核线程。线程很重（内存占用大、切换成本高），所以你不敢开几万个线程。</span></li><li fid="u3d074b21" data-lake-id="u4d2fbf41" id="u4d2fbf41"><span data-lake-id="u2d5497af" id="u2d5497af">玄铁 ：采用 M:N 模型 。 异步 { ... } 开启的是一个极其轻量级的“逻辑任务”。成千上万个任务可以跑在极少数的几个物理 CPU 核心上。</span></li></ul><h5 data-lake-id="KORC1" id="KORC1" data-lake-index-type="0"><span data-lake-id="ue83dcb82" id="ue83dcb82">解决方案的进化</span></h5><ul list="u28be98ab"><li fid="u14601e9f" data-lake-id="u649aadba" id="u649aadba"><span data-lake-id="ub371891f" id="ub371891f">传统解决方案 (C/Unix)</span></li></ul><ul list="u28be98ab" data-lake-indent="1"><li fid="u14601e9f" data-lake-id="u339eb68a" id="u339eb68a"><span data-lake-id="u3cad9c14" id="u3cad9c14">异步实现：pthread_create + 回调函数 + 互斥锁</span></li><li fid="u14601e9f" data-lake-id="u9c02ab5d" id="u9c02ab5d"><span data-lake-id="ua2fffebd" id="ua2fffebd">返回值获取：通过全局变量或复杂的信号量通知</span></li><li fid="u14601e9f" data-lake-id="ua55ca902" id="ua55ca902"><span data-lake-id="ua0bbbd67" id="ua0bbbd67">并发控制：手动写循环，逐个 join 线程</span></li></ul><ul list="u28be98ab" start="2"><li fid="u14601e9f" data-lake-id="ue3f2138f" id="ue3f2138f"><span data-lake-id="ud1f5da06" id="ud1f5da06">玄铁解决方案</span></li></ul><ul list="u28be98ab" data-lake-indent="1"><li fid="u14601e9f" data-lake-id="ua2ee699c" id="ua2ee699c"><span data-lake-id="ueb4b95ed" id="ueb4b95ed">异步实现：异步 { ... } + 等待(任务)</span></li><li fid="u14601e9f" data-lake-id="ude495de9" id="ude495de9"><span data-lake-id="ufbc22e58" id="ufbc22e58">返回值获取：任务对象自带“结果槽”， 等待 时自动阻塞取值</span></li><li fid="u14601e9f" data-lake-id="u0320f9a5" id="u0320f9a5"><span data-lake-id="ufec7e2ab" id="ufec7e2ab">并发控制：并行 { {块1}, {块2} } 一次性分发并汇总</span></li></ul></details><h4 data-lake-id="lralG" id="lralG"><br></h4><p data-lake-id="u669801f3" id="u669801f3"><br></p><h3 data-lake-id="rvZGT" id="rvZGT"><span data-lake-id="u329291e7" id="u329291e7">异常捕获 (Try/Catch)</span></h3><p data-lake-id="u50ec0eb2" id="u50ec0eb2"><span data-lake-id="u21a91348" id="u21a91348">捕获运行时错误（如除零、未定义变量）。</span></p><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22java%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%E5%B0%9D%E8%AF%95%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%2010%20%2F%200%5Cn%7D%20%E6%8D%95%E6%8D%89%20(%E9%94%99)%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20%E7%A4%BA(%5C%22%E9%94%99%E8%AF%AF%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF%3A%20%5C%22%20%26%20%E9%94%99.%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF)%5Cn%20%20%20%20%E7%A4%BA(%5C%22%E9%94%99%E8%AF%AF%E5%A0%86%E6%A0%88%3A%20%5C%22%20%26%20%E9%94%99.%E5%A0%86%E6%A0%88)%5Cn%7D%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Atrue%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22customStyle%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22id%22%3A%22nIRS5%22%7D"></card><p data-lake-id="ua6e336ce" id="ua6e336ce"><span data-lake-id="u05b98ec2" id="u05b98ec2">​</span><br></p><h3 data-lake-id="TkqNy" id="TkqNy"><span data-lake-id="ubb64a7ff" id="ubb64a7ff">原生测试框架 (v0.13.0)</span></h3><p data-lake-id="ud355e8c5" id="ud355e8c5"><span data-lake-id="u17ca2c9d" id="u17ca2c9d">玄铁内置了单元测试支持，通过 </span><code data-lake-id="u358c1953" id="u358c1953"><span data-lake-id="u2d44e009" id="u2d44e009">测试</span></code><span data-lake-id="uf45bf2a5" id="uf45bf2a5"> 关键字定义测试用例。</span></p><ul list="u2389bfa2"><li fid="ubaba64ae" data-lake-id="u2863a169" id="u2863a169"><code data-lake-id="uc13b8883" id="uc13b8883"><span data-lake-id="ubb87629b" id="ubb87629b">测试 &quot;名称&quot; { ... }</span></code><span data-lake-id="u4beefeb3" id="u4beefeb3">：定义一个命名的测试块。</span></li><li fid="ubaba64ae" data-lake-id="ua22eb64a" id="ua22eb64a"><code data-lake-id="ueff0c797" id="ueff0c797"><span data-lake-id="u73030964" id="u73030964">系统.断言(条件, [消息])</span></code><span data-lake-id="u6305ef51" id="u6305ef51">：校验条件，若为假则抛出错误并终止当前测试。</span></li></ul><card type="inline" name="codeblock" value="data:%7B%22search%22%3A%22%22%2C%22mode%22%3A%22java%22%2C%22code%22%3A%22%E6%B5%8B%E8%AF%95%20%5C%22%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E6%95%B0%E5%AD%A6%E6%A0%A1%E9%AA%8C%5C%22%20%7B%5Cn%20%20%20%20%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F.%E6%96%AD%E8%A8%80(1%20%2B%201%20%3D%3D%202%2C%20%5C%22%E5%8A%A0%E6%B3%95%E9%80%BB%E8%BE%91%E9%94%99%E8%AF%AF%5C%22)%5Cn%7D%22%2C%22autoWrap%22%3Afalse%2C%22lineNumbers%22%3Atrue%2C%22heightLimit%22%3Atrue%2C%22collapsed%22%3Afalse%2C%22hideToolbar%22%3Atrue%2C%22name%22%3A%22%22%2C%22tabSize%22%3Anull%2C%22indentWithTab%22%3Afalse%2C%22lightLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22foldLines%22%3A%5B%5D%2C%22theme%22%3A%22One%20Dark%20Pro%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22FlGZz%22%7D"></card><p data-lake-id="u17366db6" id="u17366db6"><br></p><p data-lake-id="u5f9629d6" id="u5f9629d6"><br></p><h2 data-lake-id="ZShJ0" id="ZShJ0"><span data-lake-id="u23ab830c" id="u23ab830c">6. IDE 效率工具</span></h2><p data-lake-id="u23b05234" id="u23b05234"><span data-lake-id="u0b5ed773" id="u0b5ed773">配合 </span><code data-lake-id="uc076c82e" id="uc076c82e"><span data-lake-id="u5f444852" id="u5f444852" style="color: #2F4BDA">xuantie-syntax</span></code><span data-lake-id="ue0d93940" id="ue0d93940"> 扩展，支持拼音补全，无需切换输入法：</span></p><ul list="u67496103"><li fid="uf591f2b6" data-lake-id="u092ca4c0" id="u092ca4c0"><code data-lake-id="u7c6016b2" id="u7c6016b2"><span data-lake-id="u6c322bed" id="u6c322bed">she</span></code><span data-lake-id="ucf412f49" id="ucf412f49"> -&gt; </span><code data-lake-id="ue21d4848" id="ue21d4848"><span data-lake-id="ua50cf6ca" id="ua50cf6ca">设</span></code></li><li fid="uf591f2b6" data-lake-id="udeba10fe" id="udeba10fe"><code data-lake-id="ua5e44067" id="ua5e44067"><span data-lake-id="u326810f7" id="u326810f7">ruo</span></code><span data-lake-id="u8b810c90" id="u8b810c90"> -&gt; </span><code data-lake-id="ud639d499" id="ud639d499"><span data-lake-id="u1acc0bec" id="u1acc0bec">若</span></code></li><li fid="uf591f2b6" data-lake-id="u43666617" id="u43666617"><code data-lake-id="u06ef4f06" id="u06ef4f06"><span data-lake-id="u3e3cc6dc" id="u3e3cc6dc">yi</span></code><span data-lake-id="u1783ef9d" id="u1783ef9d"> -&gt; </span><code data-lake-id="ub41f2224" id="ub41f2224"><span data-lake-id="u401c6fcc" id="u401c6fcc">抑</span></code></li><li fid="uf591f2b6" data-lake-id="u75c0a917" id="u75c0a917"><code data-lake-id="ub1c19654" id="ub1c19654"><span data-lake-id="u921bd616" id="u921bd616">fou</span></code><span data-lake-id="uba5a6cc4" id="uba5a6cc4"> -&gt; </span><code data-lake-id="u4a5e0dc7" id="u4a5e0dc7"><span data-lake-id="ub4c13f54" id="ub4c13f54">否</span></code></li><li fid="uf591f2b6" data-lake-id="u560eaff9" id="u560eaff9"><code data-lake-id="u389f7384" id="u389f7384"><span data-lake-id="ub8b9d08b" id="ub8b9d08b">han</span></code><span data-lake-id="ue916735c" id="ue916735c"> -&gt; </span><code data-lake-id="ud21cf53e" id="ud21cf53e"><span data-lake-id="u124f7758" id="u124f7758">函</span></code></li><li fid="uf591f2b6" data-lake-id="u440ce9b4" id="u440ce9b4"><code data-lake-id="u1af1d7a5" id="u1af1d7a5"><span data-lake-id="u7cc2e3f7" id="u7cc2e3f7">fan</span></code><span data-lake-id="u9043e519" id="u9043e519"> -&gt; </span><code data-lake-id="ubf6f5ba4" id="ubf6f5ba4"><span data-lake-id="ub8ccd004" id="ub8ccd004">返</span></code></li><li fid="uf591f2b6" data-lake-id="u59960543" id="u59960543"><code data-lake-id="u6b7670ad" id="u6b7670ad"><span data-lake-id="u48aa8a08" id="u48aa8a08">yin</span></code><span data-lake-id="ueee4e0c9" id="ueee4e0c9"> -&gt; </span><code data-lake-id="u28dc75e4" id="u28dc75e4"><span data-lake-id="u292e58c0" id="u292e58c0">引</span></code></li><li fid="uf591f2b6" data-lake-id="u0035d0cd" id="u0035d0cd"><code data-lake-id="ucfb7b6de" id="ucfb7b6de"><span data-lake-id="ud59e5d0d" id="ud59e5d0d">duan</span></code><span data-lake-id="u98432fd0" id="u98432fd0"> -&gt; </span><code data-lake-id="u5738a97e" id="u5738a97e"><span data-lake-id="uc3604960" id="uc3604960">断</span></code></li><li fid="uf591f2b6" data-lake-id="u27fed9c8" id="u27fed9c8"><code data-lake-id="u29d82cf1" id="u29d82cf1"><span data-lake-id="u9a380d97" id="u9a380d97">xu</span></code><span data-lake-id="u012f628a" id="u012f628a"> -&gt; </span><code data-lake-id="u7db25e12" id="u7db25e12"><span data-lake-id="ubdc22daf" id="ubdc22daf">续</span></code></li><li fid="uf591f2b6" data-lake-id="u59f7d5fd" id="u59f7d5fd"><code data-lake-id="ub52eaf0b" id="ub52eaf0b"><span data-lake-id="u21d4b9b4" id="u21d4b9b4">xun</span></code><span data-lake-id="u34a9e045" id="u34a9e045"> -&gt; </span><code data-lake-id="uf72f9a34" id="uf72f